var book = {
	"name": "Deuteronomy",
	"numChapters": 34,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>These are the words Moses spoke to all Israel in the wilderness east of the Jordan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4894A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4894A\"></sup>—that is, in the Arabah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4894B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4894B\"></sup>—opposite Suph, between Paran<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4894C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4894C\"></sup> and Tophel, Laban, Hazeroth and Dizahab.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(It takes eleven days to go from Horeb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4895D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4895D\"></sup> to Kadesh Barnea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4895E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4895E\"></sup> by the Mount Seir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4895F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4895F\"></sup> road.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4895G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4895G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the fortieth year,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4896H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4896H\"></sup> on the first day of the eleventh month,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4896I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4896I\"></sup> Moses proclaimed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4896J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4896J\"></sup> to the Israelites all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded him concerning them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This was after he had defeated Sihon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4897K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4897K\"></sup> king of the Amorites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4897L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4897L\"></sup> who reigned in Heshbon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4897M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4897M\"></sup> and at Edrei had defeated Og<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4897N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4897N\"></sup> king of Bashan, who reigned in Ashtaroth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4897O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4897O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>East of the Jordan in the territory of Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4898P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4898P\"></sup> Moses began to expound this law, saying:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God said to us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4899Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4899Q\"></sup> at Horeb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4899R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4899R\"></sup> “You have stayed long enough<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4899S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4899S\"></sup> at this mountain.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Break camp and advance into the hill country of the Amorites;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900T\"></sup> go to all the neighboring peoples in the Arabah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900U\"></sup> in the mountains, in the western foothills, in the Negev<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900V\"></sup> and along the coast, to the land of the Canaanites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900W\"></sup> and to Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900X\"></sup> as far as the great river, the Euphrates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4900Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4900Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>See, I have given you this land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4901Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4901Z\"></sup>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4901AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4901AA\"></sup> Go in and take possession of the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4901AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4901AB\"></sup> he would give to your fathers—to Abraham, Isaac and Jacob—and to their descendants after them.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>At that time I said to you, “You are too heavy a burden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4902AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4902AC\"></sup> for me to carry alone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4902AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4902AD\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has increased<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4903AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4903AE\"></sup> your numbers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4903AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4903AF\"></sup> so that today you are as numerous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4903AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4903AG\"></sup> as the stars in the sky.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4903AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4903AH\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, increase<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4904AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4904AI\"></sup> you a thousand times and bless you as he has promised!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4904AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4904AJ\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But how can I bear your problems and your burdens and your disputes all by myself?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4905AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4905AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Choose some wise, understanding and respected men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4906AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4906AL\"></sup> from each of your tribes, and I will set them over you.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You answered me, “What you propose to do is good.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So I took<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4908AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4908AM\"></sup> the leading men of your tribes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4908AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4908AN\"></sup> wise and respected men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4908AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4908AO\"></sup> and appointed them to have authority over you—as commanders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4908AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4908AP\"></sup> of thousands, of hundreds, of fifties and of tens and as tribal officials.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4908AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4908AQ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And I charged your judges at that time, “Hear the disputes between your people and judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4909AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4909AR\"></sup> fairly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4909AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4909AS\"></sup> whether the case is between two Israelites or between an Israelite and a foreigner residing among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4909AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4909AT\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not show partiality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4910AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4910AU\"></sup> in judging; hear both small and great alike. Do not be afraid of anyone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4910AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4910AV\"></sup> for judgment belongs to God. Bring me any case too hard for you, and I will hear it.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4910AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4910AW\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And at that time I told you everything you were to do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4911AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4911AX\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God commanded us, we set out from Horeb and went toward the hill country of the Amorites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4912AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4912AY\"></sup> through all that vast and dreadful wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4912AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4912AZ\"></sup> that you have seen, and so we reached Kadesh Barnea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4912BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4912BA\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then I said to you, “You have reached the hill country of the Amorites, which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God is giving us.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>See, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has given you the land. Go up and take possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4914BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4914BB\"></sup> of it as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, told you. Do not be afraid;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4914BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4914BC\"></sup> do not be discouraged.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4914BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4914BD\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then all of you came to me and said, “Let us send men ahead to spy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4915BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4915BE\"></sup> out the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4915BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4915BF\"></sup> for us and bring back a report about the route we are to take and the towns we will come to.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The idea seemed good to me; so I selected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4916BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4916BG\"></sup> twelve of you, one man from each tribe.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They left and went up into the hill country, and came to the Valley of Eshkol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4917BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4917BH\"></sup> and explored it.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Taking with them some of the fruit of the land, they brought it down to us and reported,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4918BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4918BI\"></sup> “It is a good land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4918BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4918BJ\"></sup> that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God is giving us.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4918BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4918BK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But you were unwilling to go up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4919BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4919BL\"></sup> you rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4919BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4919BM\"></sup> against the command of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You grumbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4920BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4920BN\"></sup> in your tents and said, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hates us; so he brought us out of Egypt to deliver us into the hands of the Amorites to destroy us.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Where can we go? Our brothers have made our hearts melt in fear. They say, ‘The people are stronger and taller<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4921BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4921BO\"></sup> than we are; the cities are large, with walls up to the sky. We even saw the Anakites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4921BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4921BP\"></sup> there.’”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then I said to you, “Do not be terrified; do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4922BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4922BQ\"></sup> of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4922BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4922BR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who is going before you, will fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4923BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4923BS\"></sup> for you, as he did for you in Egypt, before your very eyes,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and in the wilderness. There you saw how the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4924BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4924BT\"></sup> you, as a father carries his son, all the way you went until you reached this place.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4924BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4924BU\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>In spite of this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4925BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4925BV\"></sup> you did not trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4925BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4925BW\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>who went ahead of you on your journey, in fire by night and in a cloud by day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4926BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4926BX\"></sup> to search<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4926BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4926BY\"></sup> out places for you to camp and to show you the way you should go.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> heard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4927BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4927BZ\"></sup> what you said, he was angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4927CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4927CA\"></sup> and solemnly swore:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4927CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4927CB\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“No one from this evil generation shall see the good land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4928CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4928CC\"></sup> I swore to give your ancestors,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>except Caleb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4929CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4929CD\"></sup> son of Jephunneh. He will see it, and I will give him and his descendants the land he set his feet on, because he followed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> wholeheartedly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4929CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4929CE\"></sup>”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Because of you the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> became angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4930CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4930CF\"></sup> with me also and said, “You shall not enter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4930CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4930CG\"></sup> it, either.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But your assistant, Joshua<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4931CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4931CH\"></sup> son of Nun, will enter it. Encourage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4931CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4931CI\"></sup> him, because he will lead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4931CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4931CJ\"></sup> Israel to inherit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4931CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4931CK\"></sup> it.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And the little ones that you said would be taken captive,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4932CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4932CL\"></sup> your children who do not yet know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4932CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4932CM\"></sup> good from bad—they will enter the land. I will give it to them and they will take possession of it.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But as for you, turn around and set out toward the desert along the route to the Red Sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4933CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4933CN\"></sup>”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Then you replied, “We have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. We will go up and fight, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God commanded us.” So every one of you put on his weapons, thinking it easy to go up into the hill country.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Tell them, ‘Do not go up and fight, because I will not be with you. You will be defeated by your enemies.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4935CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4935CO\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>So I told you, but you would not listen. You rebelled against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s command and in your arrogance you marched up into the hill country.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>The Amorites who lived in those hills came out against you; they chased you like a swarm of bees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4937CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4937CP\"></sup> and beat you down from Seir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4937CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4937CQ\"></sup> all the way to Hormah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4937CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4937CR\"></sup>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>You came back and wept before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4938CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4938CS\"></sup> but he paid no attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4938CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4938CT\"></sup> to your weeping and turned a deaf ear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4938CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4938CU\"></sup> to you.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And so you stayed in Kadesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4939CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4939CV\"></sup> many days—all the time you spent there."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then we turned back and set out toward the wilderness along the route to the Red Sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4940A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4940A\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had directed me. For a long time we made our way around the hill country of Seir.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4940B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4940B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“You have made your way around this hill country long enough;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4942C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4942C\"></sup> now turn north.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Give the people these orders:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4943D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4943D\"></sup> ‘You are about to pass through the territory of your relatives the descendants of Esau,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4943E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4943E\"></sup> who live in Seir.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4943F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4943F\"></sup> They will be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4943G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4943G\"></sup> of you, but be very careful.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do not provoke them to war, for I will not give you any of their land, not even enough to put your foot on. I have given Esau the hill country of Seir as his own.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4944H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4944H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You are to pay them in silver for the food you eat and the water you drink.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has blessed you in all the work of your hands. He has watched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4946I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4946I\"></sup> over your journey through this vast wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4946J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4946J\"></sup> These forty years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4946K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4946K\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has been with you, and you have not lacked anything.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4946L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4946L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So we went on past our relatives the descendants of Esau, who live in Seir. We turned from<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4947M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4947M\"></sup> the Arabah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4947N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4947N\"></sup> road, which comes up from Elath and Ezion Geber,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4947O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4947O\"></sup> and traveled along the desert road of Moab.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4947P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4947P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Do not harass the Moabites or provoke them to war, for I will not give you any part of their land. I have given Ar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4948Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4948Q\"></sup> to the descendants of Lot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4948R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4948R\"></sup> as a possession.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>(The Emites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4949S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4949S\"></sup> used to live there—a people strong and numerous, and as tall as the Anakites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4949T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4949T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like the Anakites, they too were considered Rephaites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4950U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4950U\"></sup> but the Moabites called them Emites.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Horites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4951V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4951V\"></sup> used to live in Seir, but the descendants of Esau drove them out. They destroyed the Horites from before them and settled in their place, just as Israel did<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4951W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4951W\"></sup> in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave them as their possession.)",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Now get up and cross the Zered Valley.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4952X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4952X\"></sup>” So we crossed the valley.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thirty-eight years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4953Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4953Y\"></sup> passed from the time we left Kadesh Barnea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4953Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4953Z\"></sup> until we crossed the Zered Valley. By then, that entire generation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4953AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4953AA\"></sup> of fighting men had perished from the camp, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had sworn to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4953AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4953AB\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand was against them until he had completely eliminated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4954AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4954AC\"></sup> them from the camp.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now when the last of these fighting men among the people had died,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Today you are to pass by the region of Moab at Ar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4957AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4957AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When you come to the Ammonites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4958AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4958AE\"></sup> do not harass them or provoke them to war,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4958AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4958AF\"></sup> for I will not give you possession of any land belonging to the Ammonites. I have given it as a possession to the descendants of Lot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4958AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4958AG\"></sup>”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>(That too was considered a land of the Rephaites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4959AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4959AH\"></sup> who used to live there; but the Ammonites called them Zamzummites.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They were a people strong and numerous, and as tall as the Anakites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4960AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4960AI\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> destroyed them from before the Ammonites, who drove them out and settled in their place.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had done the same for the descendants of Esau, who lived in Seir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4961AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4961AJ\"></sup> when he destroyed the Horites from before them. They drove them out and have lived in their place to this day.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And as for the Avvites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4962AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4962AK\"></sup> who lived in villages as far as Gaza,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4962AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4962AL\"></sup> the Caphtorites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4962AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4962AM\"></sup> coming out from Caphtor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4962AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4962AN\"></sup> destroyed them and settled in their place.)",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Set out now and cross the Arnon Gorge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4963AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4963AO\"></sup> See, I have given into your hand Sihon the Amorite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4963AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4963AP\"></sup> king of Heshbon, and his country. Begin to take possession of it and engage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4963AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4963AQ\"></sup> him in battle.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>This very day I will begin to put the terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4964AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4964AR\"></sup> and fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4964AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4964AS\"></sup> of you on all the nations under heaven. They will hear reports of you and will tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4964AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4964AT\"></sup> and be in anguish because of you.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>From the Desert of Kedemoth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4965AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4965AU\"></sup> I sent messengers to Sihon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4965AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4965AV\"></sup> king of Heshbon offering peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4965AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4965AW\"></sup> and saying,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Let us pass through your country. We will stay on the main road; we will not turn aside to the right or to the left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4966AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4966AX\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Sell us food to eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4967AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4967AY\"></sup> and water to drink for their price in silver. Only let us pass through on foot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4967AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4967AZ\"></sup>—",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>as the descendants of Esau, who live in Seir, and the Moabites, who live in Ar, did for us—until we cross the Jordan into the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God is giving us.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But Sihon king of Heshbon refused to let us pass through. For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4969BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4969BA\"></sup> your God had made his spirit stubborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4969BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4969BB\"></sup> and his heart obstinate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4969BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4969BC\"></sup> in order to give him into your hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4969BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4969BD\"></sup> as he has now done.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “See, I have begun to deliver Sihon and his country over to you. Now begin to conquer and possess his land.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4970BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4970BE\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>When Sihon and all his army came out to meet us in battle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4971BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4971BF\"></sup> at Jahaz,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God delivered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4972BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4972BG\"></sup> him over to us and we struck him down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4972BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4972BH\"></sup> together with his sons and his whole army.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>At that time we took all his towns and completely destroyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4973BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4973BI\"></sup> them—men, women and children. We left no survivors.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But the livestock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4974BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4974BJ\"></sup> and the plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4974BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4974BK\"></sup> from the towns we had captured we carried off for ourselves.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>From Aroer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4975BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4975BL\"></sup> on the rim of the Arnon Gorge, and from the town in the gorge, even as far as Gilead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4975BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4975BM\"></sup> not one town was too strong for us. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God gave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4975BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4975BN\"></sup> us all of them.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But in accordance with the command of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4976BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4976BO\"></sup> you did not encroach on any of the land of the Ammonites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4976BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4976BP\"></sup> neither the land along the course of the Jabbok<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4976BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4976BQ\"></sup> nor that around the towns in the hills."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Next we turned and went up along the road toward Bashan, and Og king of Bashan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4977A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4977A\"></sup> with his whole army marched out to meet us in battle at Edrei.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4977B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4977B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4978C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4978C\"></sup> of him, for I have delivered him into your hands, along with his whole army and his land. Do to him what you did to Sihon king of the Amorites, who reigned in Heshbon.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God also gave into our hands Og king of Bashan and all his army. We struck them down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4979D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4979D\"></sup> leaving no survivors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4979E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4979E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>At that time we took all his cities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4980F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4980F\"></sup> There was not one of the sixty cities that we did not take from them—the whole region of Argob, Og’s kingdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4980G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4980G\"></sup> in Bashan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4980H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4980H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>All these cities were fortified with high walls and with gates and bars, and there were also a great many unwalled villages.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We completely destroyed them, as we had done with Sihon king of Heshbon, destroying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4982I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4982I\"></sup> every city—men, women and children.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But all the livestock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4983J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4983J\"></sup> and the plunder from their cities we carried off for ourselves.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So at that time we took from these two kings of the Amorites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4984K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4984K\"></sup> the territory east of the Jordan, from the Arnon Gorge as far as Mount Hermon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4984L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4984L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>(Hermon is called Sirion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4985M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4985M\"></sup> by the Sidonians; the Amorites call it Senir.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4985N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4985N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We took all the towns on the plateau, and all Gilead, and all Bashan as far as Salekah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4986O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4986O\"></sup> and Edrei, towns of Og’s kingdom in Bashan.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>(Og king of Bashan was the last of the Rephaites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4987P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4987P\"></sup> His bed was decorated with iron and was more than nine cubits long and four cubits wide. It is still in Rabbah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4987Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4987Q\"></sup> of the Ammonites.)",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Of the land that we took over at that time, I gave the Reubenites and the Gadites the territory north of Aroer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4988R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4988R\"></sup> by the Arnon Gorge, including half the hill country of Gilead, together with its towns.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The rest of Gilead and also all of Bashan, the kingdom of Og, I gave to the half-tribe of Manasseh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4989S\"></sup> (The whole region of Argob in Bashan used to be known as a land of the Rephaites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4989T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4990U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4990U\"></sup> a descendant of Manasseh, took the whole region of Argob as far as the border of the Geshurites and the Maakathites;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4990V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4990V\"></sup> it was named<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4990W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4990W\"></sup> after him, so that to this day Bashan is called Havvoth Jair.)",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And I gave Gilead to Makir.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4991X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4991X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But to the Reubenites and the Gadites I gave the territory extending from Gilead down to the Arnon Gorge (the middle of the gorge being the border) and out to the Jabbok River,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4992Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4992Y\"></sup> which is the border of the Ammonites.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Its western border was the Jordan in the Arabah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4993Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4993Z\"></sup> from Kinnereth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4993AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4993AA\"></sup> to the Sea of the Arabah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4993AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4993AB\"></sup> (that is, the Dead Sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4993AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4993AC\"></sup>), below the slopes of Pisgah.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I commanded you at that time: “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has given<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4994AD\"></sup> you this land to take possession of it. But all your able-bodied men, armed for battle, must cross over ahead of the other Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4994AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4994AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>However, your wives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4995AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4995AF\"></sup> your children and your livestock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4995AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4995AG\"></sup> (I know you have much livestock) may stay in the towns I have given you,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>until the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives rest to your fellow Israelites as he has to you, and they too have taken over the land that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving them across the Jordan. After that, each of you may go back to the possession I have given you.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>At that time I commanded Joshua: “You have seen with your own eyes all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has done to these two kings. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will do the same to all the kingdoms over there where you are going.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4998AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4998AH\"></sup> of them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4998AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4998AI\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God himself will fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4998AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4998AJ\"></sup> for you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>At that time I pleaded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-4999AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-4999AK\"></sup> with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you have begun to show to your servant your greatness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5000AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5000AL\"></sup> and your strong hand. For what god<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5000AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5000AM\"></sup> is there in heaven or on earth who can do the deeds and mighty works<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5000AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5000AN\"></sup> you do?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5000AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5000AO\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let me go over and see the good land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5001AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5001AP\"></sup> beyond the Jordan—that fine hill country and Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5001AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5001AQ\"></sup>”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But because of you the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5002AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5002AR\"></sup> with me and would not listen to me. “That is enough,” the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said. “Do not speak to me anymore about this matter.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Go up to the top of Pisgah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5003AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5003AS\"></sup> and look west and north and south and east.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5003AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5003AT\"></sup> Look at the land with your own eyes, since you are not going to cross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5003AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5003AU\"></sup> this Jordan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5003AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5003AV\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But commission<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5004AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5004AW\"></sup> Joshua, and encourage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5004AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5004AX\"></sup> and strengthen him, for he will lead this people across<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5004AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5004AY\"></sup> and will cause them to inherit the land that you will see.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So we stayed in the valley near Beth Peor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5005AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5005AZ\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Now, Israel, hear the decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5006A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5006A\"></sup> and laws I am about to teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5006B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5006B\"></sup> you. Follow them so that you may live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5006C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5006C\"></sup> and may go in and take possession of the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, is giving you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Do not add<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5007D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5007D\"></sup> to what I command you and do not subtract<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5007E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5007E\"></sup> from it, but keep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5007F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5007F\"></sup> the commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5007G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5007G\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God that I give you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You saw with your own eyes what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> did at Baal Peor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5008H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5008H\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God destroyed from among you everyone who followed the Baal of Peor,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but all of you who held fast to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God are still alive today.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>See, I have taught<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5010I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5010I\"></sup> you decrees and laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5010J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5010J\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God commanded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5010K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5010K\"></sup> me, so that you may follow them in the land you are entering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5010L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5010L\"></sup> to take possession of it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Observe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5011M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5011M\"></sup> them carefully, for this will show your wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5011N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5011N\"></sup> and understanding to the nations, who will hear about all these decrees and say, “Surely this great nation is a wise and understanding people.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5011O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5011O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>What other nation is so great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5012P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5012P\"></sup> as to have their gods near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5012Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5012Q\"></sup> them the way the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God is near us whenever we pray to him?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And what other nation is so great as to have such righteous decrees and laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5013R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5013R\"></sup> as this body of laws I am setting before you today?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Only be careful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5014S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5014S\"></sup> and watch yourselves closely so that you do not forget the things your eyes have seen or let them fade from your heart as long as you live. Teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5014T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5014T\"></sup> them to your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5014U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5014U\"></sup> and to their children after them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Remember the day you stood before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at Horeb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5015V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5015V\"></sup> when he said to me, “Assemble the people before me to hear my words so that they may learn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5015W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5015W\"></sup> to revere<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5015X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5015X\"></sup> me as long as they live in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5015Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5015Y\"></sup> and may teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5015Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5015Z\"></sup> them to their children.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You came near and stood at the foot of the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5016AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5016AA\"></sup> while it blazed with fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5016AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5016AB\"></sup> to the very heavens, with black clouds and deep darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5016AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5016AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5017AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5017AD\"></sup> to you out of the fire. You heard the sound of words but saw no form;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5017AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5017AE\"></sup> there was only a voice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5017AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5017AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He declared to you his covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5018AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5018AG\"></sup> the Ten Commandments,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5018AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5018AH\"></sup> which he commanded you to follow and then wrote them on two stone tablets.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> directed me at that time to teach you the decrees and laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5019AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5019AI\"></sup> you are to follow in the land that you are crossing the Jordan to possess.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You saw no form<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5020AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5020AJ\"></sup> of any kind the day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to you at Horeb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5020AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5020AK\"></sup> out of the fire. Therefore watch yourselves very carefully,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5020AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5020AL\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>so that you do not become corrupt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5021AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5021AM\"></sup> and make for yourselves an idol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5021AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5021AN\"></sup> an image of any shape, whether formed like a man or a woman,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>or like any animal on earth or any bird that flies in the air,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5022AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5022AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>or like any creature that moves along the ground or any fish in the waters below.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And when you look up to the sky and see the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5024AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5024AP\"></sup> the moon and the stars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5024AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5024AQ\"></sup>—all the heavenly array<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5024AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5024AR\"></sup>—do not be enticed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5024AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5024AS\"></sup> into bowing down to them and worshiping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5024AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5024AT\"></sup> things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has apportioned to all the nations under heaven.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But as for you, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> took you and brought you out of the iron-smelting furnace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5025AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5025AU\"></sup> out of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5025AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5025AV\"></sup> to be the people of his inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5025AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5025AW\"></sup> as you now are.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was angry with me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5026AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5026AX\"></sup> because of you, and he solemnly swore that I would not cross the Jordan and enter the good land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as your inheritance.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will die in this land;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5027AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5027AY\"></sup> I will not cross the Jordan; but you are about to cross over and take possession of that good land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5027AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5027AZ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Be careful not to forget the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5028BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5028BA\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God that he made with you; do not make for yourselves an idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5028BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5028BB\"></sup> in the form of anything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has forbidden.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is a consuming fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5029BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5029BC\"></sup> a jealous God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5029BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5029BD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>After you have had children and grandchildren and have lived in the land a long time—if you then become corrupt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5030BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5030BE\"></sup> and make any kind of idol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5030BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5030BF\"></sup> doing evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5030BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5030BG\"></sup> in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and arousing his anger,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I call the heavens and the earth as witnesses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5031BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5031BH\"></sup> against you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5031BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5031BI\"></sup> this day that you will quickly perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5031BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5031BJ\"></sup> from the land that you are crossing the Jordan to possess. You will not live there long but will certainly be destroyed.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5032BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5032BK\"></sup> you among the peoples, and only a few of you will survive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5032BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5032BL\"></sup> among the nations to which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will drive you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>There you will worship man-made gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5033BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5033BM\"></sup> of wood and stone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5033BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5033BN\"></sup> which cannot see or hear or eat or smell.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5033BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5033BO\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But if from there you seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5034BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5034BP\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, you will find him if you seek him with all your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5034BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5034BQ\"></sup> and with all your soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5034BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5034BR\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>When you are in distress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5035BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5035BS\"></sup> and all these things have happened to you, then in later days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5035BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5035BT\"></sup> you will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5035BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5035BU\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and obey him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is a merciful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5036BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5036BV\"></sup> God; he will not abandon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5036BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5036BW\"></sup> or destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5036BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5036BX\"></sup> you or forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5036BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5036BY\"></sup> the covenant with your ancestors, which he confirmed to them by oath.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Ask<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5037BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5037BZ\"></sup> now about the former days, long before your time, from the day God created human beings on the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5037CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5037CA\"></sup> ask from one end of the heavens to the other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5037CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5037CB\"></sup> Has anything so great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5037CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5037CC\"></sup> as this ever happened, or has anything like it ever been heard of?",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Has any other people heard the voice of God speaking out of fire, as you have, and lived?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5038CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5038CD\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Has any god ever tried to take for himself one nation out of another nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CE\"></sup> by testings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CF\"></sup> by signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CG\"></sup> and wonders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CH\"></sup> by war, by a mighty hand and an outstretched arm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CI\"></sup> or by great and awesome deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5039CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5039CJ\"></sup> like all the things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God did for you in Egypt before your very eyes?",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>You were shown these things so that you might know that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is God; besides him there is no other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5040CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5040CK\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>From heaven he made you hear his voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5041CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5041CL\"></sup> to discipline<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5041CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5041CM\"></sup> you. On earth he showed you his great fire, and you heard his words from out of the fire.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Because he loved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5042CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5042CN\"></sup> your ancestors and chose their descendants after them, he brought you out of Egypt by his Presence and his great strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5042CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5042CO\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>to drive out before you nations greater and stronger than you and to bring you into their land to give it to you for your inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5043CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5043CP\"></sup> as it is today.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5044CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5044CQ\"></sup> and take to heart this day that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is God in heaven above and on the earth below. There is no other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5044CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5044CR\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Keep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5045CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5045CS\"></sup> his decrees and commands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5045CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5045CT\"></sup> which I am giving you today, so that it may go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5045CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5045CU\"></sup> with you and your children after you and that you may live long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5045CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5045CV\"></sup> in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives you for all time.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Then Moses set aside three cities east of the Jordan,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>to which anyone who had killed a person could flee if they had unintentionally<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5047CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5047CX\"></sup> killed a neighbor without malice aforethought. They could flee into one of these cities and save their life.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>The cities were these: Bezer in the wilderness plateau, for the Reubenites; Ramoth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5048CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5048CY\"></sup> in Gilead, for the Gadites; and Golan in Bashan, for the Manassites.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>This is the law Moses set before the Israelites.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>These are the stipulations, decrees and laws Moses gave them when they came out of Egypt",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>and were in the valley near Beth Peor east of the Jordan, in the land of Sihon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5051CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5051CZ\"></sup> king of the Amorites, who reigned in Heshbon and was defeated by Moses and the Israelites as they came out of Egypt.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>They took possession of his land and the land of Og king of Bashan, the two Amorite kings east of the Jordan.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>This land extended from Aroer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5053DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5053DA\"></sup> on the rim of the Arnon Gorge to Mount Sirion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5053DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5053DB\"></sup> (that is, Hermon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5053DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5053DC\"></sup>),",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>and included all the Arabah east of the Jordan, as far as the Dead Sea, below the slopes of Pisgah."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Moses summoned all Israel and said:Hear, Israel, the decrees and laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5055B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5055B\"></sup> I declare in your hearing today. Learn them and be sure to follow them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God made a covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5056C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5056C\"></sup> with us at Horeb.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5056D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It was not with our ancestors that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> made this covenant, but with us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5057E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5057E\"></sup> with all of us who are alive here today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5057F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5058G\"></sup> to you face to face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5058H\"></sup> out of the fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5058I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5058I\"></sup> on the mountain.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>(At that time I stood between<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5059J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5059J\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and you to declare to you the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, because you were afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5059K\"></sup> of the fire and did not go up the mountain.) And he said:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who brought you out of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5060L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5060L\"></sup> out of the land of slavery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5060M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5060M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“You shall have no other gods before me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“You shall not make for yourself an image in the form of anything in heaven above or on the earth beneath or in the waters below.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5062N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5062N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You shall not bow down to them or worship them; for I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, am a jealous God, punishing the children for the sin of the parents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5063O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5063O\"></sup> to the third and fourth generation of those who hate me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5063P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5063P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but showing love to a thousand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5064Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5064Q\"></sup> generations of those who love me and keep my commandments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5064R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5064R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“You shall not misuse the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5065S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5065S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not hold anyone guiltless who misuses his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5065T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5065T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Observe the Sabbath day by keeping it holy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5066U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5066U\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Six days you shall labor and do all your work,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but the seventh day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5068V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5068V\"></sup> is a sabbath to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God. On it you shall not do any work, neither you, nor your son or daughter, nor your male or female servant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5068W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5068W\"></sup> nor your ox, your donkey or any of your animals, nor any foreigner residing in your towns, so that your male and female servants may rest, as you do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5068X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5068X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Remember that you were slaves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5069Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5069Y\"></sup> in Egypt and that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God brought you out of there with a mighty hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5069Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5069Z\"></sup> and an outstretched arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5069AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5069AA\"></sup> Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you to observe the Sabbath day.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Honor your father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5070AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5070AB\"></sup> and your mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5070AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5070AC\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you, so that you may live long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5070AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5070AD\"></sup> and that it may go well with you in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“You shall not murder.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5071AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5071AE\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“You shall not commit adultery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5072AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5072AF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“You shall not steal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5073AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5073AG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“You shall not give false testimony against your neighbor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5074AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5074AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“You shall not covet your neighbor’s wife. You shall not set your desire on your neighbor’s house or land, his male or female servant, his ox or donkey, or anything that belongs to your neighbor.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5075AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5075AI\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>These are the commandments the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> proclaimed in a loud voice to your whole assembly there on the mountain from out of the fire, the cloud and the deep darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5076AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5076AJ\"></sup> and he added nothing more. Then he wrote them on two stone tablets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5076AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5076AK\"></sup> and gave them to me.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When you heard the voice out of the darkness, while the mountain was ablaze with fire, all the leaders of your tribes and your elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5077AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5077AL\"></sup> came to me.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And you said, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has shown us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5078AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5078AM\"></sup> his glory and his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5078AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5078AN\"></sup> and we have heard his voice from the fire. Today we have seen that a person can live even if God speaks with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5078AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5078AO\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But now, why should we die? This great fire will consume us, and we will die if we hear the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God any longer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5079AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5079AP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For what mortal has ever heard the voice of the living God speaking out of fire, as we have, and survived?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5080AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5080AQ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Go near and listen to all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God says.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5081AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5081AR\"></sup> Then tell us whatever the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God tells you. We will listen and obey.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5081AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5081AS\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> heard you when you spoke to me, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “I have heard what this people said to you. Everything they said was good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5082AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5082AT\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Oh, that their hearts would be inclined to fear me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5083AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5083AU\"></sup> and keep all my commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5083AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5083AV\"></sup> always, so that it might go well with them and their children forever!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5083AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5083AW\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Go, tell them to return to their tents.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But you stay here<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5085AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5085AX\"></sup> with me so that I may give you all the commands, decrees and laws you are to teach them to follow in the land I am giving them to possess.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So be careful to do what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5086AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5086AY\"></sup> do not turn aside to the right or to the left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5086AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5086AZ\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Walk in obedience to all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5087BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5087BA\"></sup> so that you may live and prosper and prolong your days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5087BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5087BB\"></sup> in the land that you will possess."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>These are the commands, decrees and laws the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God directed me to teach you to observe in the land that you are crossing the Jordan to possess,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>so that you, your children and their children after them may fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5089A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5089A\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God as long as you live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5089B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5089B\"></sup> by keeping all his decrees and commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5089C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5089C\"></sup> that I give you, and so that you may enjoy long life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5089D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5089D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Hear, Israel, and be careful to obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5090E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5090E\"></sup> so that it may go well with you and that you may increase greatly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5090F\"></sup> in a land flowing with milk and honey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5090G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5090G\"></sup> just as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5090H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5090H\"></sup> you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear, O Israel: The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5091I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5091I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5092J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5092J\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God with all your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5092K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5092K\"></sup> and with all your soul and with all your strength.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5092L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5092L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>These commandments that I give you today are to be on your hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5093M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5093M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Impress them on your children. Talk about them when you sit at home and when you walk along the road, when you lie down and when you get up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5094N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5094N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Tie them as symbols on your hands and bind them on your foreheads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5095O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5095O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Write them on the doorframes of your houses and on your gates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5096P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5096P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God brings you into the land he swore to your fathers, to Abraham, Isaac and Jacob, to give you—a land with large, flourishing cities you did not build,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5097Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5097Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>houses filled with all kinds of good things you did not provide, wells you did not dig,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5098R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5098R\"></sup> and vineyards and olive groves you did not plant—then when you eat and are satisfied,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5098S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5098S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>be careful that you do not forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5099T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5099T\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who brought you out of Egypt, out of the land of slavery.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5100U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5100U\"></sup> your God, serve him only<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5100V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5100V\"></sup> and take your oaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5100W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5100W\"></sup> in his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5100X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5100X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not follow other gods, the gods of the peoples around you;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5102Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5102Y\"></sup>, who is among you, is a jealous God and his anger will burn against you, and he will destroy you from the face of the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do not put the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God to the test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5103Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5103Z\"></sup> as you did at Massah.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Be sure to keep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5104AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5104AA\"></sup> the commands of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and the stipulations and decrees he has given you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5104AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5104AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Do what is right and good in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s sight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5105AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5105AC\"></sup> so that it may go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5105AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5105AD\"></sup> with you and you may go in and take over the good land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> promised on oath to your ancestors,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>thrusting out all your enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5106AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5106AE\"></sup> before you, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In the future, when your son asks you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5107AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5107AF\"></sup> “What is the meaning of the stipulations, decrees and laws the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has commanded you?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>tell him: “We were slaves of Pharaoh in Egypt, but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought us out of Egypt with a mighty hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5108AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5108AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Before our eyes the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent signs and wonders—great and terrible—on Egypt and Pharaoh and his whole household.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But he brought us out from there to bring us in and give us the land he promised on oath to our ancestors.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded us to obey all these decrees and to fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5111AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5111AH\"></sup> so that we might always prosper and be kept alive, as is the case today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5111AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5111AI\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And if we are careful to obey all this law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5112AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5112AJ\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, as he has commanded us, that will be our righteousness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5112AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5112AK\"></sup>”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God brings you into the land you are entering to possess<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113A\"></sup> and drives out before you many nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113B\"></sup>—the Hittites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113C\"></sup> Girgashites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113D\"></sup> Amorites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113E\"></sup> Canaanites, Perizzites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113F\"></sup> Hivites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113G\"></sup> and Jebusites,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5113H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5113H\"></sup> seven nations larger and stronger than you—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has delivered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5114I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5114I\"></sup> them over to you and you have defeated them, then you must destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5114J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5114J\"></sup> them totally.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5114K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5114K\"></sup> Make no treaty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5114L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5114L\"></sup> with them, and show them no mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5114M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5114M\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not intermarry with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5115N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5115N\"></sup> Do not give your daughters to their sons or take their daughters for your sons,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for they will turn your children away from following me to serve other gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5116O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5116O\"></sup> and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger will burn against you and will quickly destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5116P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5116P\"></sup> you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what you are to do to them: Break down their altars, smash their sacred stones, cut down their Asherah poles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5117Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5117Q\"></sup> and burn their idols in the fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5117R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5117R\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For you are a people holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5118S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5118S\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5118T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5118T\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5118U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5118U\"></sup> you out of all the peoples on the face of the earth to be his people, his treasured possession.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5118V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5118V\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> did not set his affection on you and choose you because you were more numerous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5119W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5119W\"></sup> than other peoples, for you were the fewest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5119X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5119X\"></sup> of all peoples.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5119Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5119Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But it was because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5120Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5120Z\"></sup> you and kept the oath he swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5120AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5120AA\"></sup> to your ancestors that he brought you out with a mighty hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5120AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5120AB\"></sup> and redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5120AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5120AC\"></sup> you from the land of slavery,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5120AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5120AD\"></sup> from the power of Pharaoh king of Egypt.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Know therefore that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5121AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5121AE\"></sup> he is the faithful God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5121AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5121AF\"></sup> keeping his covenant of love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5121AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5121AG\"></sup> to a thousand generations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5121AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5121AH\"></sup> of those who love him and keep his commandments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5121AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5121AI\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Butthose who hate him he will repay to their face by destruction;he will not be slow to repay to their face those who hate him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5122AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5122AJ\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore, take care to follow the commands, decrees and laws I give you today.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you pay attention to these laws and are careful to follow them, then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will keep his covenant of love with you, as he swore to your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5124AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5124AK\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He will love you and bless you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AL\"></sup> and increase your numbers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AM\"></sup> He will bless the fruit of your womb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AN\"></sup> the crops of your land—your grain, new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AO\"></sup> and olive oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AP\"></sup>—the calves of your herds and the lambs of your flocks in the land he swore to your ancestors to give you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5125AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5125AQ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You will be blessed more than any other people; none of your men or women will be childless, nor will any of your livestock be without young.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5126AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5126AR\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will keep you free from every disease.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5127AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5127AS\"></sup> He will not inflict on you the horrible diseases you knew in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5127AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5127AT\"></sup> but he will inflict them on all who hate you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5127AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5127AU\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You must destroy all the peoples the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives over to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5128AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5128AV\"></sup> Do not look on them with pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5128AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5128AW\"></sup> and do not serve their gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5128AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5128AX\"></sup> for that will be a snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5128AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5128AY\"></sup> to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You may say to yourselves, “These nations are stronger than we are. How can we drive them out?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5129AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5129AZ\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5130BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5130BA\"></sup> of them; remember well what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God did to Pharaoh and to all Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5130BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5130BB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You saw with your own eyes the great trials, the signs and wonders, the mighty hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5131BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5131BC\"></sup> and outstretched arm, with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God brought you out. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will do the same to all the peoples you now fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5131BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5131BD\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Moreover, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will send the hornet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5132BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5132BE\"></sup> among them until even the survivors who hide from you have perished.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not be terrified by them, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who is among you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5133BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5133BF\"></sup> is a great and awesome God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5133BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5133BG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will drive out those nations before you, little by little.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5134BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5134BH\"></sup> You will not be allowed to eliminate them all at once, or the wild animals will multiply around you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will deliver them over to you, throwing them into great confusion until they are destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5135BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5135BI\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He will give their kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5136BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5136BJ\"></sup> into your hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5136BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5136BK\"></sup> and you will wipe out their names from under heaven. No one will be able to stand up against you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5136BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5136BL\"></sup> you will destroy them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5136BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5136BM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The images of their gods you are to burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5137BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5137BN\"></sup> in the fire. Do not covet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5137BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5137BO\"></sup> the silver and gold on them, and do not take it for yourselves, or you will be ensnared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5137BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5137BP\"></sup> by it, for it is detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5137BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5137BQ\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do not bring a detestable thing into your house or you, like it, will be set apart for destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5138BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5138BR\"></sup> Regard it as vile and utterly detest it, for it is set apart for destruction."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Be careful to follow every command I am giving you today, so that you may live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5139A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5139A\"></sup> and increase and may enter and possess the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> promised on oath to your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5139B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5139B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Remember how the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God led<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5140C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5140C\"></sup> you all the way in the wilderness these forty years, to humble and test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5140D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5140D\"></sup> you in order to know what was in your heart, whether or not you would keep his commands.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He humbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141E\"></sup> you, causing you to hunger and then feeding you with manna,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141F\"></sup> which neither you nor your ancestors had known, to teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141G\"></sup> you that man does not live on bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141H\"></sup> alone but on every word that comes from the mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141I\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5141J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5141J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your clothes did not wear out and your feet did not swell during these forty years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5142K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5142K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Know then in your heart that as a man disciplines his son, so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God disciplines you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5143L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5143L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Observe the commands of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, walking in obedience to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5144M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5144M\"></sup> and revering him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5144N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5144N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is bringing you into a good land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5145O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5145O\"></sup>—a land with brooks, streams, and deep springs gushing out into the valleys and hills;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5145P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5145P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>a land with wheat and barley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5146Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5146Q\"></sup> vines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5146R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5146R\"></sup> and fig trees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5146S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5146S\"></sup> pomegranates, olive oil and honey;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5146T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5146T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>a land where bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5147U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5147U\"></sup> will not be scarce and you will lack nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5147V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5147V\"></sup> a land where the rocks are iron and you can dig copper out of the hills.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5147W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5147W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When you have eaten and are satisfied,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5148X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5148X\"></sup> praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God for the good land he has given you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Be careful that you do not forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5149Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5149Y\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, failing to observe his commands, his laws and his decrees that I am giving you this day.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Otherwise, when you eat and are satisfied, when you build fine houses and settle down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5150Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5150Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and when your herds and flocks grow large and your silver and gold increase and all you have is multiplied,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then your heart will become proud and you will forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5152AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5152AA\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who brought you out of Egypt, out of the land of slavery.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He led you through the vast and dreadful wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5153AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5153AB\"></sup> that thirsty and waterless land, with its venomous snakes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5153AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5153AC\"></sup> and scorpions. He brought you water out of hard rock.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5153AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5153AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He gave you manna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5154AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5154AE\"></sup> to eat in the wilderness, something your ancestors had never known,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5154AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5154AF\"></sup> to humble and test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5154AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5154AG\"></sup> you so that in the end it might go well with you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You may say to yourself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5155AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5155AH\"></sup> “My power and the strength of my hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5155AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5155AI\"></sup> have produced this wealth for me.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But remember the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, for it is he who gives you the ability to produce wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5156AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5156AJ\"></sup> and so confirms his covenant, which he swore to your ancestors, as it is today.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If you ever forget the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and follow other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5157AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5157AK\"></sup> and worship and bow down to them, I testify against you today that you will surely be destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5157AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5157AL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Like the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5158AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5158AM\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> destroyed before you, so you will be destroyed for not obeying the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5158AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5158AN\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Hear, Israel: You are now about to cross the Jordan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5159A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5159A\"></sup> to go in and dispossess nations greater and stronger than you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5159B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5159B\"></sup> with large cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5159C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5159C\"></sup> that have walls up to the sky.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5159D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5159D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The people are strong and tall—Anakites! You know about them and have heard it said: “Who can stand up against the Anakites?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5160E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5160E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But be assured today that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is the one who goes across ahead of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5161F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5161F\"></sup> like a devouring fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5161G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5161G\"></sup> He will destroy them; he will subdue them before you. And you will drive them out and annihilate them quickly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5161H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5161H\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has promised you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>After the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has driven them out before you, do not say to yourself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5162I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5162I\"></sup> “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought me here to take possession of this land because of my righteousness.” No, it is on account of the wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5162J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5162J\"></sup> of these nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5162K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5162K\"></sup> that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is going to drive them out before you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It is not because of your righteousness or your integrity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163L\"></sup> that you are going in to take possession of their land; but on account of the wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163M\"></sup> of these nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163N\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will drive them out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163O\"></sup> before you, to accomplish what he swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163P\"></sup> to your fathers, to Abraham, Isaac and Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5163Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5163Q\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Understand, then, that it is not because of your righteousness that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you this good land to possess, for you are a stiff-necked people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5164R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5164R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember this and never forget how you aroused the anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5165S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5165S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in the wilderness. From the day you left Egypt until you arrived here, you have been rebellious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5165T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5165T\"></sup> against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5165U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5165U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>At Horeb you aroused the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5166V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5166V\"></sup> so that he was angry enough to destroy you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5166W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5166W\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When I went up on the mountain to receive the tablets of stone, the tablets of the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5167X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5167X\"></sup> that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had made with you, I stayed on the mountain forty days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5167Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5167Y\"></sup> and forty nights; I ate no bread and drank no water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5167Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5167Z\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave me two stone tablets inscribed by the finger of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5168AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5168AA\"></sup> On them were all the commandments the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> proclaimed to you on the mountain out of the fire, on the day of the assembly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5168AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5168AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At the end of the forty days and forty nights,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5169AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5169AC\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave me the two stone tablets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5169AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5169AD\"></sup> the tablets of the covenant.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> told me, “Go down from here at once, because your people whom you brought out of Egypt have become corrupt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5170AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5170AE\"></sup> They have turned away quickly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5170AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5170AF\"></sup> from what I commanded them and have made an idol for themselves.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “I have seen this people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5171AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5171AG\"></sup>, and they are a stiff-necked people indeed!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Let me alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5172AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5172AH\"></sup> so that I may destroy them and blot out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5172AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5172AI\"></sup> their name from under heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5172AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5172AJ\"></sup> And I will make you into a nation stronger and more numerous than they.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So I turned and went down from the mountain while it was ablaze with fire. And the two tablets of the covenant were in my hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5173AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5173AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When I looked, I saw that you had sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God; you had made for yourselves an idol cast in the shape of a calf.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5174AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5174AL\"></sup> You had turned aside quickly from the way that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So I took the two tablets and threw them out of my hands, breaking them to pieces before your eyes.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then once again I fell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5176AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5176AM\"></sup> prostrate before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for forty days and forty nights; I ate no bread and drank no water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5176AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5176AN\"></sup> because of all the sin you had committed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5176AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5176AO\"></sup> doing what was evil in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s sight and so arousing his anger.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I feared the anger and wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for he was angry enough with you to destroy you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5177AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5177AP\"></sup> But again the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> listened to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5177AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5177AQ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was angry enough with Aaron to destroy him, but at that time I prayed for Aaron too.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Also I took that sinful thing of yours, the calf you had made, and burned it in the fire. Then I crushed it and ground it to powder as fine as dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5179AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5179AR\"></sup> and threw the dust into a stream that flowed down the mountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5179AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5179AS\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You also made the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5180AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5180AT\"></sup> at Taberah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5180AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5180AU\"></sup> at Massah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5180AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5180AV\"></sup> and at Kibroth Hattaavah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5180AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5180AW\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent you out from Kadesh Barnea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5181AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5181AX\"></sup> he said, “Go up and take possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5181AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5181AY\"></sup> of the land I have given you.” But you rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5181AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5181AZ\"></sup> against the command of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God. You did not trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5181BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5181BA\"></sup> him or obey him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You have been rebellious against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> ever since I have known you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5182BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5182BB\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I lay prostrate before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> those forty days and forty nights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5183BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5183BC\"></sup> because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had said he would destroy you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5183BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5183BD\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and said, “Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do not destroy your people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5184BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5184BE\"></sup> your own inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5184BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5184BF\"></sup> that you redeemed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5184BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5184BG\"></sup> by your great power and brought out of Egypt with a mighty hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5184BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5184BH\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Remember your servants Abraham, Isaac and Jacob. Overlook the stubbornness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5185BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5185BI\"></sup> of this people, their wickedness and their sin.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Otherwise, the country<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5186BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5186BJ\"></sup> from which you brought us will say, ‘Because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was not able to take them into the land he had promised them, and because he hated them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5186BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5186BK\"></sup> he brought them out to put them to death in the wilderness.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5186BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5186BL\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But they are your people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5187BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5187BM\"></sup> your inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5187BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5187BN\"></sup> that you brought out by your great power and your outstretched arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5187BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5187BO\"></sup>”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>At that time the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Chisel out two stone tablets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5188A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5188A\"></sup> like the first ones and come up to me on the mountain. Also make a wooden ark.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will write on the tablets the words that were on the first tablets, which you broke. Then you are to put them in the ark.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5189B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5189B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I made the ark out of acacia wood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5190C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5190C\"></sup> and chiseled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5190D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5190D\"></sup> out two stone tablets like the first ones, and I went up on the mountain with the two tablets in my hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> wrote on these tablets what he had written before, the Ten Commandments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5191E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5191E\"></sup> he had proclaimed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5191F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5191F\"></sup> to you on the mountain, out of the fire, on the day of the assembly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5191G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5191G\"></sup> And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave them to me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I came back down the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5192H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5192H\"></sup> and put the tablets in the ark<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5192I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5192I\"></sup> I had made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5192J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5192J\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded me, and they are there now.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5192K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5192K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>(The Israelites traveled from the wells of Bene Jaakan to Moserah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5193L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5193L\"></sup> There Aaron died<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5193M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5193M\"></sup> and was buried, and Eleazar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5193N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5193N\"></sup> his son succeeded him as priest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5193O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5193O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>From there they traveled to Gudgodah and on to Jotbathah, a land with streams of water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5194P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5194P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>At that time the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> set apart the tribe of Levi<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5195Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5195Q\"></sup> to carry the ark of the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5195R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5195R\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to stand before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5195S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5195S\"></sup> and to pronounce blessings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5195T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5195T\"></sup> in his name, as they still do today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5195U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5195U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>That is why the Levites have no share or inheritance among their fellow Israelites; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is their inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5196V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5196V\"></sup> as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God told them.)",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now I had stayed on the mountain forty days and forty nights, as I did the first time, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> listened to me at this time also. It was not his will to destroy you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5197W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5197W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Go,” the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “and lead the people on their way, so that they may enter and possess the land I swore to their ancestors to give them.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And now, Israel, what does the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God ask of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199X\"></sup> but to fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199Y\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, to walk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199Z\"></sup> in obedience to him, to love him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199AA\"></sup> to serve the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199AB\"></sup> your God with all your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199AC\"></sup> and with all your soul,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5199AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5199AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and to observe the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5200AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5200AE\"></sup> and decrees that I am giving you today for your own good?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5200AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5200AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>To the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God belong the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5201AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5201AG\"></sup> even the highest heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5201AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5201AH\"></sup> the earth and everything in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5201AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5201AI\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yet the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> set his affection on your ancestors and loved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5202AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5202AJ\"></sup> them, and he chose you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5202AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5202AK\"></sup> their descendants, above all the nations—as it is today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5202AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5202AL\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Circumcise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5203AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5203AM\"></sup> your hearts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5203AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5203AN\"></sup> therefore, and do not be stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5203AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5203AO\"></sup> any longer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is God of gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5204AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5204AP\"></sup> and Lord of lords,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5204AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5204AQ\"></sup> the great God, mighty and awesome,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5204AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5204AR\"></sup> who shows no partiality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5204AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5204AS\"></sup> and accepts no bribes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5204AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5204AT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He defends the cause of the fatherless and the widow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5205AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5205AU\"></sup> and loves the foreigner residing among you, giving them food and clothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5205AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5205AV\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And you are to love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5206AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5206AW\"></sup> those who are foreigners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5206AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5206AX\"></sup> for you yourselves were foreigners in Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5206AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5206AY\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and serve him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5207AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5207AZ\"></sup> Hold fast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5207BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5207BA\"></sup> to him and take your oaths in his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5207BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5207BB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He is the one you praise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5208BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5208BC\"></sup> he is your God, who performed for you those great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5208BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5208BD\"></sup> and awesome wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5208BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5208BE\"></sup> you saw with your own eyes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your ancestors who went down into Egypt were seventy in all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5209BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5209BF\"></sup> and now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has made you as numerous as the stars in the sky.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5209BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5209BG\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5210A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5210A\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and keep his requirements, his decrees, his laws and his commands always.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5210B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5210B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Remember today that your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5211C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5211C\"></sup> were not the ones who saw and experienced the discipline of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5211D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5211D\"></sup> his majesty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5211E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5211E\"></sup> his mighty hand, his outstretched arm;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5211F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5211F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the signs he performed and the things he did in the heart of Egypt, both to Pharaoh king of Egypt and to his whole country;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5212G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5212G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>what he did to the Egyptian army, to its horses and chariots,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5213H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5213H\"></sup> how he overwhelmed them with the waters of the Red Sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5213I\"></sup> as they were pursuing you, and how the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought lasting ruin on them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It was not your children who saw what he did for you in the wilderness until you arrived at this place,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and what he did<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5215J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5215J\"></sup> to Dathan and Abiram, sons of Eliab the Reubenite, when the earth opened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5215K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5215K\"></sup> its mouth right in the middle of all Israel and swallowed them up with their households, their tents and every living thing that belonged to them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But it was your own eyes that saw all these great things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5216L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5216L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Observe therefore all the commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5217M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5217M\"></sup> I am giving you today, so that you may have the strength to go in and take over the land that you are crossing the Jordan to possess,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5217N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5217N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and so that you may live long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5218O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5218O\"></sup> in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5218P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5218P\"></sup> to your ancestors to give to them and their descendants, a land flowing with milk and honey.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5218Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5218Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The land you are entering to take over is not like the land of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5219R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5219R\"></sup> from which you have come, where you planted your seed and irrigated it by foot as in a vegetable garden.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the land you are crossing the Jordan to take possession of is a land of mountains and valleys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5220S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5220S\"></sup> that drinks rain from heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5220T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5220T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is a land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God cares for; the eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5221U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5221U\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God are continually on it from the beginning of the year to its end.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So if you faithfully obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5222V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5222V\"></sup> the commands I am giving you today—to love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5222W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5222W\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and to serve him with all your heart and with all your soul<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5222X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5222X\"></sup>—",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then I will send rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5223Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5223Y\"></sup> on your land in its season, both autumn and spring rains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5223Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5223Z\"></sup> so that you may gather in your grain, new wine and olive oil.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will provide grass<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5224AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5224AA\"></sup> in the fields for your cattle, and you will eat and be satisfied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5224AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5224AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Be careful, or you will be enticed to turn away and worship other gods and bow down to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5225AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5225AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5226AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5226AD\"></sup> will burn against you, and he will shut up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5226AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5226AE\"></sup> the heavens so that it will not rain and the ground will yield no produce,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5226AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5226AF\"></sup> and you will soon perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5226AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5226AG\"></sup> from the good land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is giving you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Fix these words of mine in your hearts and minds; tie them as symbols on your hands and bind them on your foreheads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5227AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5227AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Teach them to your children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5228AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5228AI\"></sup> talking about them when you sit at home and when you walk along the road, when you lie down and when you get up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5228AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5228AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Write them on the doorframes of your houses and on your gates,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5229AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5229AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>so that your days and the days of your children may be many<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5230AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5230AL\"></sup> in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> swore to give your ancestors, as many as the days that the heavens are above the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5230AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5230AM\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If you carefully observe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5231AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5231AN\"></sup> all these commands I am giving you to follow—to love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5231AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5231AO\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, to walk in obedience to him and to hold fast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5231AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5231AP\"></sup> to him—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will drive out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5232AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5232AQ\"></sup> all these nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5232AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5232AR\"></sup> before you, and you will dispossess nations larger and stronger than you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5232AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5232AS\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Every place where you set your foot will be yours:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5233AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5233AT\"></sup> Your territory will extend from the desert to Lebanon, and from the Euphrates River<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5233AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5233AU\"></sup> to the Mediterranean Sea.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>No one will be able to stand against you. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, as he promised you, will put the terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5234AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5234AV\"></sup> and fear of you on the whole land, wherever you go.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5234AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5234AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>See, I am setting before you today a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5235AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5235AX\"></sup> and a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5235AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5235AY\"></sup>—",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>the blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5236AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5236AZ\"></sup> if you obey the commands of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God that I am giving you today;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>the curse if you disobey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5237BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5237BA\"></sup> the commands of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and turn from the way that I command you today by following other gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5237BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5237BB\"></sup> which you have not known.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has brought you into the land you are entering to possess, you are to proclaim on Mount Gerizim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5238BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5238BC\"></sup> the blessings, and on Mount Ebal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5238BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5238BD\"></sup> the curses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5238BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5238BE\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>As you know, these mountains are across the Jordan, westward, toward the setting sun, near the great trees of Moreh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5239BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5239BF\"></sup> in the territory of those Canaanites living in the Arabah in the vicinity of Gilgal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5239BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5239BG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>You are about to cross the Jordan to enter and take possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5240BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5240BH\"></sup> of the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5240BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5240BI\"></sup> you. When you have taken it over and are living there,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>be sure that you obey all the decrees and laws I am setting before you today."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>These are the decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5242A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5242A\"></sup> and laws you must be careful to follow in the land that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, has given you to possess—as long as you live in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5242B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5242B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Destroy completely all the places on the high mountains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5243C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5243C\"></sup> on the hills and under every spreading tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5243D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5243D\"></sup> where the nations you are dispossessing worship their gods.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Break down their altars, smash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5244E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5244E\"></sup> their sacred stones and burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5244F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5244F\"></sup> their Asherah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5244G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5244G\"></sup> poles in the fire; cut down the idols of their gods and wipe out their names<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5244H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5244H\"></sup> from those places.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You must not worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in their way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5245I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5245I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you are to seek the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose from among all your tribes to put his Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5246J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5246J\"></sup> there for his dwelling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5246K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5246K\"></sup> To that place you must go;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>there bring your burnt offerings and sacrifices, your tithes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5247L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5247L\"></sup> and special gifts, what you have vowed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5247M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5247M\"></sup> to give and your freewill offerings, and the firstborn of your herds and flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5247N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5247N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There, in the presence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5248O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5248O\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, you and your families shall eat and shall rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5248P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5248P\"></sup> in everything you have put your hand to, because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has blessed you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You are not to do as we do here today, everyone doing as they see fit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5249Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5249Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>since you have not yet reached the resting place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5250R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5250R\"></sup> and the inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5250S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5250S\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But you will cross the Jordan and settle in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5251T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5251T\"></sup> you as an inheritance, and he will give you rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5251U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5251U\"></sup> from all your enemies around you so that you will live in safety.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose as a dwelling for his Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5252V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5252V\"></sup>—there you are to bring everything I command you: your burnt offerings and sacrifices, your tithes and special gifts, and all the choice possessions you have vowed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5252W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5252W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And there rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5253X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5253X\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God—you, your sons and daughters, your male and female servants, and the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5253Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5253Y\"></sup> from your towns who have no allotment or inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5253Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5253Z\"></sup> of their own.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Be careful not to sacrifice your burnt offerings anywhere you please.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5254AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5254AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Offer them only at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5255AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5255AB\"></sup> in one of your tribes, and there observe everything I command you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Nevertheless, you may slaughter your animals in any of your towns and eat as much of the meat as you want, as if it were gazelle or deer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5256AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5256AC\"></sup> according to the blessing the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives you. Both the ceremonially unclean and the clean may eat it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But you must not eat the blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5257AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5257AD\"></sup> pour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5257AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5257AE\"></sup> it out on the ground like water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5257AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5257AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You must not eat in your own towns the tithe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5258AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5258AG\"></sup> of your grain and new wine and olive oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5258AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5258AH\"></sup> or the firstborn of your herds and flocks, or whatever you have vowed to give,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5258AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5258AI\"></sup> or your freewill offerings or special gifts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5258AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5258AJ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Instead, you are to eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5259AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5259AK\"></sup> them in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5259AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5259AL\"></sup>—you, your sons and daughters, your male and female servants, and the Levites from your towns—and you are to rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5259AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5259AM\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in everything you put your hand to.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Be careful not to neglect the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5260AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5260AN\"></sup> as long as you live in your land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5260AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5260AO\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has enlarged your territory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5261AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5261AP\"></sup> as he promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5261AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5261AQ\"></sup> you, and you crave meat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5261AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5261AR\"></sup> and say, “I would like some meat,” then you may eat as much of it as you want.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If the place where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God chooses to put his Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5262AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5262AS\"></sup> is too far away from you, you may slaughter animals from the herds and flocks the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given you, as I have commanded you, and in your own towns you may eat as much of them as you want.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5262AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5262AT\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Eat them as you would gazelle or deer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5263AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5263AU\"></sup> Both the ceremonially unclean and the clean may eat.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But be sure you do not eat the blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5264AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5264AV\"></sup> because the blood is the life, and you must not eat the life with the meat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5264AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5264AW\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You must not eat the blood; pour it out on the ground like water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5265AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5265AX\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not eat it, so that it may go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5266AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5266AY\"></sup> with you and your children after you, because you will be doing what is right<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5266AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5266AZ\"></sup> in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But take your consecrated things and whatever you have vowed to give,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5267BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5267BA\"></sup> and go to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Present your burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5268BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5268BB\"></sup> on the altar of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, both the meat and the blood. The blood of your sacrifices must be poured beside the altar of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, but you may eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5268BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5268BC\"></sup> the meat.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Be careful to obey all these regulations I am giving you, so that it may always go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5269BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5269BD\"></sup> with you and your children after you, because you will be doing what is good and right in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will cut off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5270BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5270BE\"></sup> before you the nations you are about to invade and dispossess. But when you have driven them out and settled in their land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5270BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5270BF\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and after they have been destroyed before you, be careful not to be ensnared<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5271BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5271BG\"></sup> by inquiring about their gods, saying, “How do these nations serve their gods? We will do the same.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5271BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5271BH\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>You must not worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in their way, because in worshiping their gods, they do all kinds of detestable things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5272BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5272BI\"></sup> They even burn their sons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5272BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5272BJ\"></sup> and daughters in the fire as sacrifices to their gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5272BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5272BK\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>See that you do all I command you; do not add<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5273BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5273BL\"></sup> to it or take away from it."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>If a prophet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5274A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5274A\"></sup> or one who foretells by dreams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5274B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5274B\"></sup> appears among you and announces to you a sign or wonder,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and if the sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5275C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5275C\"></sup> or wonder spoken of takes place, and the prophet says, “Let us follow other gods”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5275D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5275D\"></sup> (gods you have not known) “and let us worship them,”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>you must not listen to the words of that prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5276E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5276E\"></sup> or dreamer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5276F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5276F\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is testing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5276G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5276G\"></sup> you to find out whether you love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5276H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5276H\"></sup> him with all your heart and with all your soul.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God you must follow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5277I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5277I\"></sup> and him you must revere.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5277J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5277J\"></sup> Keep his commands and obey him; serve him and hold fast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5277K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5277K\"></sup> to him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>That prophet or dreamer must be put to death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5278L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5278L\"></sup> for inciting rebellion against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who brought you out of Egypt and redeemed you from the land of slavery. That prophet or dreamer tried to turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5278M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5278M\"></sup> you from the way the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God commanded you to follow. You must purge the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5278N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5278N\"></sup> from among you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If your very own brother, or your son or daughter, or the wife you love, or your closest friend secretly entices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5279O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5279O\"></sup> you, saying, “Let us go and worship other gods”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5279P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5279P\"></sup> (gods that neither you nor your ancestors have known,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>gods of the peoples around you, whether near or far, from one end of the land to the other),",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>do not yield<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5281Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5281Q\"></sup> to them or listen to them. Show them no pity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5281R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5281R\"></sup> Do not spare them or shield them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You must certainly put them to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5282S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5282S\"></sup> Your hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5282T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5282T\"></sup> must be the first in putting them to death, and then the hands of all the people.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Stone them to death, because they tried to turn you away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5283U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5283U\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who brought you out of Egypt, out of the land of slavery.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then all Israel will hear and be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5284V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5284V\"></sup> and no one among you will do such an evil thing again.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If you hear it said about one of the towns the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you to live in",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>that troublemakers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5286W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5286W\"></sup> have arisen among you and have led the people of their town astray, saying, “Let us go and worship other gods” (gods you have not known),",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>then you must inquire, probe and investigate it thoroughly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5287X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5287X\"></sup> And if it is true and it has been proved that this detestable thing has been done among you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5287Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5287Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>you must certainly put to the sword all who live in that town. You must destroy it completely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5288Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5288Z\"></sup> both its people and its livestock.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5288AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5288AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You are to gather all the plunder of the town into the middle of the public square and completely burn the town<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5289AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5289AB\"></sup> and all its plunder as a whole burnt offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5289AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5289AC\"></sup> That town is to remain a ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5289AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5289AD\"></sup> forever, never to be rebuilt,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and none of the condemned things are to be found in your hands. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will turn from his fierce anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5290AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5290AE\"></sup> will show you mercy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5290AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5290AF\"></sup> and will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5290AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5290AG\"></sup> on you. He will increase your numbers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5290AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5290AH\"></sup> as he promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5290AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5290AI\"></sup> on oath to your ancestors—",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>because you obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God by keeping all his commands that I am giving you today and doing what is right<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5291AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5291AJ\"></sup> in his eyes."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>You are the children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5292B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5292B\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God. Do not cut yourselves or shave the front of your heads for the dead,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for you are a people holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5293C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5293C\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5293D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5293D\"></sup> Out of all the peoples on the face of the earth, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has chosen you to be his treasured possession.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5293E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5293E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not eat any detestable thing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5294F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5294F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are the animals you may eat:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5295G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5295G\"></sup> the ox, the sheep, the goat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5295H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5295H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>the deer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5296I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5296I\"></sup> the gazelle, the roe deer, the wild goat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5296J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5296J\"></sup> the ibex, the antelope and the mountain sheep.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You may eat any animal that has a divided hoof and that chews the cud.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>However, of those that chew the cud or that have a divided hoof you may not eat the camel, the rabbit or the hyrax. Although they chew the cud, they do not have a divided hoof; they are ceremonially unclean for you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The pig is also unclean; although it has a divided hoof, it does not chew the cud. You are not to eat their meat or touch their carcasses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5299K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5299K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Of all the creatures living in the water, you may eat any that has fins and scales.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But anything that does not have fins and scales you may not eat; for you it is unclean.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You may eat any clean bird.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But these you may not eat: the eagle, the vulture, the black vulture,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>the red kite, the black kite, any kind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5304L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5304L\"></sup> of falcon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5304M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5304M\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>any kind of raven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5305N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5305N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>the horned owl, the screech owl, the gull, any kind of hawk,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>the little owl, the great owl, the white owl,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>the desert owl,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5308O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5308O\"></sup> the osprey, the cormorant,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>the stork, any kind of heron, the hoopoe and the bat.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>All flying insects are unclean to you; do not eat them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But any winged creature that is clean you may eat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5311P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5311P\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not eat anything you find already dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5312Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5312Q\"></sup> You may give it to the foreigner residing in any of your towns, and they may eat it, or you may sell it to any other foreigner. But you are a people holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5312R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5312R\"></sup>Do not cook a young goat in its mother’s milk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5312S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5312S\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Be sure to set aside a tenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5313T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5313T\"></sup> of all that your fields produce each year.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5314U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5314U\"></sup> the tithe of your grain, new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5314V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5314V\"></sup> and olive oil, and the firstborn of your herds and flocks in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place he will choose as a dwelling for his Name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5314W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5314W\"></sup> so that you may learn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5314X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5314X\"></sup> to revere<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5314Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5314Y\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God always.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But if that place is too distant and you have been blessed by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and cannot carry your tithe (because the place where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose to put his Name is so far away),",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>then exchange<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5316Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5316Z\"></sup> your tithe for silver, and take the silver with you and go to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Use the silver to buy whatever you like: cattle, sheep, wine or other fermented drink,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5317AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5317AA\"></sup> or anything you wish. Then you and your household shall eat there in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and rejoice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5317AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5317AB\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And do not neglect the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5318AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5318AC\"></sup> living in your towns, for they have no allotment or inheritance of their own.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5318AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5318AD\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>At the end of every three years, bring all the tithes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5319AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5319AE\"></sup> of that year’s produce and store it in your towns,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5319AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5319AF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>so that the Levites (who have no allotment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5320AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5320AG\"></sup> or inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5320AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5320AH\"></sup> of their own) and the foreigners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5320AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5320AI\"></sup> the fatherless and the widows who live in your towns may come and eat and be satisfied,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5320AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5320AJ\"></sup> and so that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God may bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5320AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5320AK\"></sup> you in all the work of your hands."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>At the end of every seven years you must cancel debts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5321B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5321B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is how it is to be done: Every creditor shall cancel any loan they have made to a fellow Israelite. They shall not require payment from anyone among their own people, because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s time for canceling debts has been proclaimed.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You may require payment from a foreigner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5323C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5323C\"></sup> but you must cancel any debt your fellow Israelite owes you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>However, there need be no poor people among you, for in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you to possess as your inheritance, he will richly bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5324D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5324D\"></sup> you,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>if only you fully obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and are careful to follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5325E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5325E\"></sup> all these commands I am giving you today.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless you as he has promised, and you will lend to many nations but will borrow from none. You will rule over many nations but none will rule over you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5326F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5326F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If anyone is poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5327G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5327G\"></sup> among your fellow Israelites in any of the towns of the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you, do not be hardhearted or tightfisted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5327H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5327H\"></sup> toward them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Rather, be openhanded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5328I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5328I\"></sup> and freely lend them whatever they need.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Be careful not to harbor this wicked thought: “The seventh year, the year for canceling debts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5329J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5329J\"></sup> is near,” so that you do not show ill will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5329K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5329K\"></sup> toward the needy among your fellow Israelites and give them nothing. They may then appeal to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> against you, and you will be found guilty of sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5329L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5329L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Give generously to them and do so without a grudging heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5330M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5330M\"></sup> then because of this the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5330N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5330N\"></sup> you in all your work and in everything you put your hand to.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There will always be poor people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5331O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5331O\"></sup> in the land. Therefore I command you to be openhanded toward your fellow Israelites who are poor and needy in your land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5331P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5331P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If any of your people—Hebrew men or women—sell themselves to you and serve you six years, in the seventh year you must let them go free.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5332S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5332S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when you release them, do not send them away empty-handed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Supply them liberally from your flock, your threshing floor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5334T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5334T\"></sup> and your winepress. Give to them as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has blessed you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Remember that you were slaves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5335U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5335U\"></sup> in Egypt and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God redeemed you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5335V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5335V\"></sup> That is why I give you this command today.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But if your servant says to you, “I do not want to leave you,” because he loves you and your family and is well off with you,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>then take an awl and push it through his earlobe into the door, and he will become your servant for life. Do the same for your female servant.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Do not consider it a hardship to set your servant free, because their service to you these six years has been worth twice as much as that of a hired hand. And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless you in everything you do.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Set apart for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5339W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5339W\"></sup> your God every firstborn male<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5339X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5339X\"></sup> of your herds and flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5339Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5339Y\"></sup> Do not put the firstborn of your cows to work, and do not shear the firstborn of your sheep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5339Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5339Z\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Each year you and your family are to eat them in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place he will choose.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5340AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5340AA\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If an animal has a defect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5341AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5341AB\"></sup> is lame or blind, or has any serious flaw, you must not sacrifice it to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5341AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5341AC\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You are to eat it in your own towns. Both the ceremonially unclean and the clean may eat it, as if it were gazelle or deer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5342AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5342AD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But you must not eat the blood; pour it out on the ground like water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5343AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5343AE\"></sup>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Observe the month of Aviv<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5344B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5344B\"></sup> and celebrate the Passover<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5344C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5344C\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, because in the month of Aviv he brought you out of Egypt by night.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Sacrifice as the Passover to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God an animal from your flock or herd at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose as a dwelling for his Name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5345D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5345D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do not eat it with bread made with yeast, but for seven days eat unleavened bread, the bread of affliction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5346E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5346E\"></sup> because you left Egypt in haste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5346F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5346F\"></sup>—so that all the days of your life you may remember the time of your departure from Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5346G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5346G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let no yeast be found in your possession in all your land for seven days. Do not let any of the meat you sacrifice on the evening<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5347H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5347H\"></sup> of the first day remain until morning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5347I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5347I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You must not sacrifice the Passover in any town the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives you",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>except in the place he will choose as a dwelling for his Name. There you must sacrifice the Passover in the evening, when the sun goes down, on the anniversary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5349J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5349J\"></sup> of your departure from Egypt.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Roast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5350K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5350K\"></sup> it and eat it at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose. Then in the morning return to your tents.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For six days eat unleavened bread and on the seventh day hold an assembly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5351L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5351L\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and do no work.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5351M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5351M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Count off seven weeks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5352O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5352O\"></sup> from the time you begin to put the sickle to the standing grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5352P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5352P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then celebrate the Festival of Weeks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God by giving a freewill offering in proportion to the blessings the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has given you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5354Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5354Q\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place he will choose as a dwelling for his Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5354R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5354R\"></sup>—you, your sons and daughters, your male and female servants, the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5354S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5354S\"></sup> in your towns, and the foreigners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5354T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5354T\"></sup> the fatherless and the widows living among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5354U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5354U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Remember that you were slaves in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5355V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5355V\"></sup> and follow carefully these decrees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Celebrate the Festival of Tabernacles for seven days after you have gathered the produce of your threshing floor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5356X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5356X\"></sup> and your winepress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5356Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5356Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Be joyful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5357Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5357Z\"></sup> at your festival—you, your sons and daughters, your male and female servants, and the Levites, the foreigners, the fatherless and the widows who live in your towns.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For seven days celebrate the festival to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose. For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless you in all your harvest and in all the work of your hands, and your joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5358AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5358AA\"></sup> will be complete.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Three times a year all your men must appear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5359AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5359AB\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place he will choose: at the Festival of Unleavened Bread,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5359AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5359AC\"></sup> the Festival of Weeks and the Festival of Tabernacles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5359AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5359AD\"></sup> No one should appear before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> empty-handed:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5359AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5359AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Each of you must bring a gift in proportion to the way the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has blessed you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Appoint judges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5361AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5361AF\"></sup> and officials for each of your tribes in every town the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you, and they shall judge the people fairly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5361AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5361AG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not pervert justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5362AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5362AH\"></sup> or show partiality.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5362AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5362AI\"></sup> Do not accept a bribe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5362AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5362AJ\"></sup> for a bribe blinds the eyes of the wise and twists the words of the innocent.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Follow justice and justice alone, so that you may live and possess the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not set up any wooden Asherah pole<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5364AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5364AK\"></sup> beside the altar you build to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5364AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5364AL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and do not erect a sacred stone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5365AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5365AM\"></sup> for these the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God hates."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Do not sacrifice to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God an ox or a sheep that has any defect<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5366A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5366A\"></sup> or flaw in it, for that would be detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5366B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5366B\"></sup> to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5366C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5366C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If a man or woman living among you in one of the towns the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives you is found doing evil in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in violation of his covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5367D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5367D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and contrary to my command<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5368E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5368E\"></sup> has worshiped other gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5368F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5368F\"></sup> bowing down to them or to the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5368G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5368G\"></sup> or the moon or the stars in the sky,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5368H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5368H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and this has been brought to your attention, then you must investigate it thoroughly. If it is true<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5369I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5369I\"></sup> and it has been proved that this detestable thing has been done in Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5369J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5369J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>take the man or woman who has done this evil deed to your city gate and stone that person to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5370K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5370K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the testimony of two or three witnesses a person is to be put to death, but no one is to be put to death on the testimony of only one witness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5371L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5371L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The hands of the witnesses must be the first in putting that person to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5372M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5372M\"></sup> and then the hands of all the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5372N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5372N\"></sup> You must purge the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5372O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5372O\"></sup> from among you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If cases come before your courts that are too difficult for you to judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5373P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5373P\"></sup>—whether bloodshed, lawsuits or assaults<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5373Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5373Q\"></sup>—take them to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5373R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5373R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Go to the Levitical<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5374S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5374S\"></sup> priests and to the judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5374T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5374T\"></sup> who is in office at that time. Inquire of them and they will give you the verdict.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5374U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5374U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>You must act according to the decisions they give you at the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose. Be careful to do everything they instruct you to do.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Act according to whatever they teach you and the decisions they give you. Do not turn aside from what they tell you, to the right or to the left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5376V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5376V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Anyone who shows contempt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5377W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5377W\"></sup> for the judge or for the priest who stands ministering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5377X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5377X\"></sup> there to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is to be put to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5377Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5377Y\"></sup> You must purge the evil from Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5377Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5377Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>All the people will hear and be afraid, and will not be contemptuous again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5378AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5378AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When you enter the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you and have taken possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5379AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5379AB\"></sup> of it and settled in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5379AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5379AC\"></sup> and you say, “Let us set a king over us like all the nations around us,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5379AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5379AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>be sure to appoint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5380AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5380AE\"></sup> over you a king the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God chooses. He must be from among your fellow Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5380AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5380AF\"></sup> Do not place a foreigner over you, one who is not an Israelite.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The king, moreover, must not acquire great numbers of horses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5381AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5381AG\"></sup> for himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5381AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5381AH\"></sup> or make the people return to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5381AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5381AI\"></sup> to get more of them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5381AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5381AJ\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has told you, “You are not to go back that way again.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5381AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5381AK\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He must not take many wives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5382AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5382AL\"></sup> or his heart will be led astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5382AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5382AM\"></sup> He must not accumulate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5382AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5382AN\"></sup> large amounts of silver and gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5382AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5382AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When he takes the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5383AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5383AP\"></sup> of his kingdom, he is to write<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5383AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5383AQ\"></sup> for himself on a scroll a copy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5383AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5383AR\"></sup> of this law, taken from that of the Levitical priests.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It is to be with him, and he is to read it all the days of his life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5384AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5384AS\"></sup> so that he may learn to revere the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> his God and follow carefully all the words of this law and these decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5384AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5384AT\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and not consider himself better than his fellow Israelites and turn from the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5385AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5385AU\"></sup> to the right or to the left.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5385AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5385AV\"></sup> Then he and his descendants will reign a long time over his kingdom in Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5385AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5385AW\"></sup>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>The Levitical<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5386A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5386A\"></sup> priests—indeed, the whole tribe of Levi—are to have no allotment or inheritance with Israel. They shall live on the food offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5386B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5386B\"></sup> presented to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for that is their inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5386C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5386C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They shall have no inheritance among their fellow Israelites; the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is their inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5387D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5387D\"></sup> as he promised them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5387E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5387E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is the share due the priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5388F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5388F\"></sup> from the people who sacrifice a bull<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5388G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5388G\"></sup> or a sheep: the shoulder, the internal organs and the meat from the head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5388H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5388H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You are to give them the firstfruits of your grain, new wine and olive oil, and the first wool from the shearing of your sheep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5389I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5389I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has chosen them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5390J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5390J\"></sup> and their descendants out of all your tribes to stand and minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5390K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5390K\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s name always.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5390L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5390L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If a Levite moves from one of your towns anywhere in Israel where he is living, and comes in all earnestness to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will choose,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5391M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5391M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>he may minister in the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5392N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5392N\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> his God like all his fellow Levites who serve there in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He is to share equally in their benefits, even though he has received money from the sale of family possessions.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5393O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5393O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When you enter the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you, do not learn to imitate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5394P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5394P\"></sup> the detestable ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5394Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5394Q\"></sup> of the nations there.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Let no one be found among you who sacrifices their son or daughter in the fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5395R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5395R\"></sup> who practices divination<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5395S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5395S\"></sup> or sorcery,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5395T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5395T\"></sup> interprets omens, engages in witchcraft,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5395U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5395U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>or casts spells,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5396V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5396V\"></sup> or who is a medium or spiritist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5396W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5396W\"></sup> or who consults the dead.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Anyone who does these things is detestable to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; because of these same detestable practices the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will drive out those nations before you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5397X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5397X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You must be blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5398Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5398Y\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5398Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5398Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The nations you will dispossess listen to those who practice sorcery or divination.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5399AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5399AA\"></sup> But as for you, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has not permitted you to do so.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will raise up for you a prophet like me from among you, from your fellow Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5400AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5400AB\"></sup> You must listen to him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For this is what you asked of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at Horeb on the day of the assembly when you said, “Let us not hear the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God nor see this great fire anymore, or we will die.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5401AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5401AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “What they say is good.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will raise up for them a prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5403AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5403AD\"></sup> like you from among their fellow Israelites, and I will put my words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5403AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5403AE\"></sup> in his mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5403AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5403AF\"></sup> He will tell them everything I command him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5403AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5403AG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I myself will call to account<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5404AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5404AH\"></sup> anyone who does not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5404AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5404AI\"></sup> to my words that the prophet speaks in my name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5404AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5404AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But a prophet who presumes to speak in my name anything I have not commanded, or a prophet who speaks in the name of other gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5405AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5405AK\"></sup> is to be put to death.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5405AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5405AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You may say to yourselves, “How can we know when a message has not been spoken by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If what a prophet proclaims in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not take place or come true,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5407AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5407AM\"></sup> that is a message the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5407AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5407AN\"></sup> That prophet has spoken presumptuously,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5407AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5407AO\"></sup> so do not be alarmed."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has destroyed the nations whose land he is giving you, and when you have driven them out and settled in their towns and houses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5408B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5408B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>then set aside for yourselves three cities in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you to possess.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Determine the distances involved and divide into three parts the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as an inheritance, so that a person who kills someone may flee for refuge to one of these cities.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is the rule concerning anyone who kills a person and flees there for safety—anyone who kills a neighbor unintentionally, without malice aforethought.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For instance, a man may go into the forest with his neighbor to cut wood, and as he swings his ax to fell a tree, the head may fly off and hit his neighbor and kill him. That man may flee to one of these cities and save his life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Otherwise, the avenger of blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5413C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5413C\"></sup> might pursue him in a rage, overtake him if the distance is too great, and kill him even though he is not deserving of death, since he did it to his neighbor without malice aforethought.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>This is why I command you to set aside for yourselves three cities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God enlarges your territory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5415D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5415D\"></sup> as he promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5415E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5415E\"></sup> on oath to your ancestors, and gives you the whole land he promised them,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>because you carefully follow all these laws I command you today—to love the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and to walk always in obedience to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5416F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5416F\"></sup>—then you are to set aside three more cities.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do this so that innocent blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5417G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5417G\"></sup> will not be shed in your land, which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as your inheritance, and so that you will not be guilty of bloodshed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5417H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5417H\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But if out of hate someone lies in wait, assaults and kills a neighbor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5418I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5418I\"></sup> and then flees to one of these cities,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>the killer shall be sent for by the town elders, be brought back from the city, and be handed over to the avenger of blood to die.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Show no pity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5420J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5420J\"></sup> You must purge from Israel the guilt of shedding innocent blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5420K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5420K\"></sup> so that it may go well with you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not move your neighbor’s boundary stone set up by your predecessors in the inheritance you receive in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you to possess.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5421L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5421L\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>One witness is not enough to convict anyone accused of any crime or offense they may have committed. A matter must be established by the testimony of two or three witnesses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5422M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5422M\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If a malicious witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5423N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5423N\"></sup> takes the stand to accuse someone of a crime,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>the two people involved in the dispute must stand in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> before the priests and the judges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5424O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5424O\"></sup> who are in office at the time.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The judges must make a thorough investigation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5425P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5425P\"></sup> and if the witness proves to be a liar, giving false testimony against a fellow Israelite,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>then do to the false witness as that witness intended to do to the other party.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5426Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5426Q\"></sup> You must purge the evil from among you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The rest of the people will hear of this and be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5427R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5427R\"></sup> and never again will such an evil thing be done among you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Show no pity:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5428S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5428S\"></sup> life for life, eye for eye, tooth for tooth, hand for hand, foot for foot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5428T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5428T\"></sup>"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>When you go to war against your enemies and see horses and chariots and an army greater than yours,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5429A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5429A\"></sup> do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5429B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5429B\"></sup> of them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5429C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5429C\"></sup> because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who brought you up out of Egypt, will be with<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5429D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5429D\"></sup> you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When you are about to go into battle, the priest shall come forward and address the army.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He shall say: “Hear, Israel: Today you are going into battle against your enemies. Do not be fainthearted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5431E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5431E\"></sup> or afraid; do not panic or be terrified by them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is the one who goes with you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5432F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5432F\"></sup> to fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5432G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5432G\"></sup> for you against your enemies to give you victory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5432H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5432H\"></sup>”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The officers shall say to the army: “Has anyone built a new house and not yet begun to live in<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5433I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5433I\"></sup> it? Let him go home, or he may die in battle and someone else may begin to live in it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Has anyone planted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5434J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5434J\"></sup> a vineyard and not begun to enjoy it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5434K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5434K\"></sup> Let him go home, or he may die in battle and someone else enjoy it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Has anyone become pledged to a woman and not married her? Let him go home, or he may die in battle and someone else marry her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5435L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5435L\"></sup>”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the officers shall add, “Is anyone afraid or fainthearted? Let him go home so that his fellow soldiers will not become disheartened too.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5436M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5436M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When the officers have finished speaking to the army, they shall appoint commanders over it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When you march up to attack a city, make its people an offer of peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5438N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5438N\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they accept and open their gates, all the people in it shall be subject<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5439O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5439O\"></sup> to forced labor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5439P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5439P\"></sup> and shall work for you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If they refuse to make peace and they engage you in battle, lay siege to that city.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God delivers it into your hand, put to the sword all the men in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5441Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5441Q\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As for the women, the children, the livestock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5442R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5442R\"></sup> and everything else in the city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5442S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5442S\"></sup> you may take these as plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5442T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5442T\"></sup> for yourselves. And you may use the plunder the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives you from your enemies.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This is how you are to treat all the cities that are at a distance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5443U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5443U\"></sup> from you and do not belong to the nations nearby.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>However, in the cities of the nations the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as an inheritance, do not leave alive anything that breathes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5444V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5444V\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Completely destroy them—the Hittites, Amorites, Canaanites, Perizzites, Hivites and Jebusites—as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has commanded you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Otherwise, they will teach you to follow all the detestable things they do in worshiping their gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5446W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5446W\"></sup> and you will sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5446X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5446X\"></sup> against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When you lay siege to a city for a long time, fighting against it to capture it, do not destroy its trees by putting an ax to them, because you can eat their fruit. Do not cut them down. Are the trees people, that you should besiege them?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>However, you may cut down trees that you know are not fruit trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5448Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5448Y\"></sup> and use them to build siege works until the city at war with you falls."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>If someone is found slain, lying in a field in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you to possess, and it is not known who the killer was,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5449A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5449A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>your elders and judges shall go out and measure the distance from the body to the neighboring towns.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the elders of the town nearest the body shall take a heifer that has never been worked and has never worn a yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5451B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5451B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and lead it down to a valley that has not been plowed or planted and where there is a flowing stream. There in the valley they are to break the heifer’s neck.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Levitical priests shall step forward, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has chosen them to minister and to pronounce blessings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5453C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5453C\"></sup> in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and to decide all cases of dispute and assault.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5453D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5453D\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then all the elders of the town nearest the body shall wash their hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5454E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5454E\"></sup> over the heifer whose neck was broken in the valley,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and they shall declare: “Our hands did not shed this blood, nor did our eyes see it done.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Accept this atonement for your people Israel, whom you have redeemed, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and do not hold your people guilty of the blood of an innocent person.” Then the bloodshed will be atoned for,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5456F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5456F\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and you will have purged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5457G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5457G\"></sup> from yourselves the guilt of shedding innocent blood, since you have done what is right in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When you go to war against your enemies and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God delivers them into your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5458H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5458H\"></sup> and you take captives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5458I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5458I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>if you notice among the captives a beautiful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5459J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5459J\"></sup> woman and are attracted to her,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5459K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5459K\"></sup> you may take her as your wife.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Bring her into your home and have her shave her head,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5460L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5460L\"></sup> trim her nails",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and put aside the clothes she was wearing when captured. After she has lived in your house and mourned her father and mother for a full month,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5461M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5461M\"></sup> then you may go to her and be her husband and she shall be your wife.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If you are not pleased with her, let her go wherever she wishes. You must not sell her or treat her as a slave, since you have dishonored her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5462N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5462N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If a man has two wives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5463O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5463O\"></sup> and he loves one but not the other, and both bear him sons but the firstborn is the son of the wife he does not love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5463P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5463P\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>when he wills his property to his sons, he must not give the rights of the firstborn to the son of the wife he loves in preference to his actual firstborn, the son of the wife he does not love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5464Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5464Q\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He must acknowledge the son of his unloved wife as the firstborn by giving him a double<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5465R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5465R\"></sup> share of all he has. That son is the first sign of his father’s strength.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5465S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5465S\"></sup> The right of the firstborn belongs to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5465T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5465T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If someone has a stubborn and rebellious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5466U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5466U\"></sup> son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5466V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5466V\"></sup> who does not obey his father and mother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5466W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5466W\"></sup> and will not listen to them when they discipline him,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>his father and mother shall take hold of him and bring him to the elders at the gate of his town.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They shall say to the elders, “This son of ours is stubborn and rebellious. He will not obey us. He is a glutton and a drunkard.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then all the men of his town are to stone him to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5469X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5469X\"></sup> You must purge the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5469Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5469Y\"></sup> from among you. All Israel will hear of it and be afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5469Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5469Z\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If someone guilty of a capital offense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5470AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5470AA\"></sup> is put to death and their body is exposed on a pole,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>you must not leave the body hanging on the pole overnight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5471AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5471AB\"></sup> Be sure to bury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5471AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5471AC\"></sup> it that same day, because anyone who is hung on a pole is under God’s curse.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5471AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5471AD\"></sup> You must not desecrate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5471AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5471AE\"></sup> the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as an inheritance."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>If you see your fellow Israelite’s ox or sheep straying, do not ignore it but be sure to take it back to its owner.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5472A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5472A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If they do not live near you or if you do not know who owns it, take it home with you and keep it until they come looking for it. Then give it back.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do the same if you find their donkey or cloak or anything else they have lost. Do not ignore it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If you see your fellow Israelite’s donkey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5475B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5475B\"></sup> or ox fallen on the road, do not ignore it. Help the owner get it to its feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5475C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5475C\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A woman must not wear men’s clothing, nor a man wear women’s clothing, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God detests anyone who does this.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If you come across a bird’s nest beside the road, either in a tree or on the ground, and the mother is sitting on the young or on the eggs, do not take the mother with the young.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5477D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5477D\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You may take the young, but be sure to let the mother go,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5478E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5478E\"></sup> so that it may go well with you and you may have a long life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5478F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5478F\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When you build a new house, make a parapet around your roof so that you may not bring the guilt of bloodshed on your house if someone falls from the roof.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5479G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5479G\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not plant two kinds of seed in your vineyard;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5480H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5480H\"></sup> if you do, not only the crops you plant but also the fruit of the vineyard will be defiled.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not plow with an ox and a donkey yoked together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5481I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5481I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Do not wear clothes of wool and linen woven together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5482J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5482J\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Make tassels on the four corners of the cloak you wear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5483K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5483K\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If a man takes a wife and, after sleeping with her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5484L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5484L\"></sup>, dislikes her",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and slanders her and gives her a bad name, saying, “I married this woman, but when I approached her, I did not find proof of her virginity,”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>then the young woman’s father and mother shall bring to the town elders at the gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5486M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5486M\"></sup> proof that she was a virgin.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Her father will say to the elders, “I gave my daughter in marriage to this man, but he dislikes her.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now he has slandered her and said, ‘I did not find your daughter to be a virgin.’ But here is the proof of my daughter’s virginity.” Then her parents shall display the cloth before the elders of the town,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5489N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5489N\"></sup> shall take the man and punish him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They shall fine him a hundred shekels of silver and give them to the young woman’s father, because this man has given an Israelite virgin a bad name. She shall continue to be his wife; he must not divorce her as long as he lives.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If, however, the charge is true<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5491O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5491O\"></sup> and no proof of the young woman’s virginity can be found,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>she shall be brought to the door of her father’s house and there the men of her town shall stone her to death. She has done an outrageous thing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5492P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5492P\"></sup> in Israel by being promiscuous while still in her father’s house. You must purge the evil from among you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If a man is found sleeping with another man’s wife, both the man who slept<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5493Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5493Q\"></sup> with her and the woman must die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5493R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5493R\"></sup> You must purge the evil from Israel.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If a man happens to meet in a town a virgin pledged to be married and he sleeps with her,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>you shall take both of them to the gate of that town and stone them to death—the young woman because she was in a town and did not scream for help, and the man because he violated another man’s wife. You must purge the evil from among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5495S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5495S\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But if out in the country a man happens to meet a young woman pledged to be married and rapes her, only the man who has done this shall die.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do nothing to the woman; she has committed no sin deserving death. This case is like that of someone who attacks and murders a neighbor,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for the man found the young woman out in the country, and though the betrothed woman screamed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5498T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5498T\"></sup> there was no one to rescue her.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>If a man happens to meet a virgin who is not pledged to be married and rapes her and they are discovered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5499U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5499U\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>he shall pay her father fifty shekels of silver. He must marry the young woman, for he has violated her. He can never divorce her as long as he lives.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>A man is not to marry his father’s wife; he must not dishonor his father’s bed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5501V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5501V\"></sup>"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>No one who has been emasculated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5502A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5502A\"></sup> by crushing or cutting may enter the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>No one born of a forbidden marriage nor any of their descendants may enter the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, not even in the tenth generation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>No Ammonite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5504B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5504B\"></sup> or Moabite or any of their descendants may enter the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, not even in the tenth generation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5504C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5504C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For they did not come to meet you with bread and water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5505D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5505D\"></sup> on your way when you came out of Egypt, and they hired Balaam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5505E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5505E\"></sup> son of Beor from Pethor in Aram Naharaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5505F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5505F\"></sup> to pronounce a curse on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5505G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5505G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>However, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God would not listen to Balaam but turned the curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5506H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5506H\"></sup> into a blessing for you, because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God loves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5506I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5506I\"></sup> you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not seek a treaty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5507J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5507J\"></sup> of friendship with them as long as you live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5507K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5507K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Do not despise an Edomite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5508L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5508L\"></sup> for the Edomites are related to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5508M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5508M\"></sup> Do not despise an Egyptian, because you resided as foreigners in their country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5508N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5508N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The third generation of children born to them may enter the assembly of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When you are encamped against your enemies, keep away from everything impure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5510O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5510O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If one of your men is unclean because of a nocturnal emission, he is to go outside the camp and stay there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5511P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5511P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But as evening approaches he is to wash himself, and at sunset<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5512Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5512Q\"></sup> he may return to the camp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5512R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5512R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Designate a place outside the camp where you can go to relieve yourself.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>As part of your equipment have something to dig with, and when you relieve yourself, dig a hole and cover up your excrement.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God moves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5515S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5515S\"></sup> about in your camp to protect you and to deliver your enemies to you. Your camp must be holy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5515T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5515T\"></sup> so that he will not see among you anything indecent and turn away from you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If a slave has taken refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5516U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5516U\"></sup> with you, do not hand them over to their master.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5516V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5516V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let them live among you wherever they like and in whatever town they choose. Do not oppress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5517W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5517W\"></sup> them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>No Israelite man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5518X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5518X\"></sup> or woman is to become a shrine prostitute.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5518Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5518Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You must not bring the earnings of a female prostitute or of a male prostitute into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God to pay any vow, because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God detests them both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5519Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5519Z\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do not charge a fellow Israelite interest, whether on money or food or anything else that may earn interest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5520AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5520AA\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You may charge a foreigner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5521AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5521AB\"></sup> interest, but not a fellow Israelite, so that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God may bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5521AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5521AC\"></sup> you in everything you put your hand to in the land you are entering to possess.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If you make a vow to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, do not be slow to pay it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5522AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5522AD\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will certainly demand it of you and you will be guilty of sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5522AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5522AE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But if you refrain from making a vow, you will not be guilty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5523AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5523AF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whatever your lips utter you must be sure to do, because you made your vow freely to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God with your own mouth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>If you enter your neighbor’s vineyard, you may eat all the grapes you want, but do not put any in your basket.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If you enter your neighbor’s grainfield, you may pick kernels with your hands, but you must not put a sickle to their standing grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5526AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5526AG\"></sup>"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>If a man marries a woman who becomes displeasing to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5527A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5527A\"></sup> because he finds something indecent about her, and he writes her a certificate of divorce,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5527B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5527B\"></sup> gives it to her and sends her from his house,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and if after she leaves his house she becomes the wife of another man,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and her second husband dislikes her and writes her a certificate of divorce, gives it to her and sends her from his house, or if he dies,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>then her first husband, who divorced her, is not allowed to marry her again after she has been defiled. That would be detestable in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Do not bring sin upon the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5530C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5530C\"></sup> your God is giving you as an inheritance.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If a man has recently married, he must not be sent to war or have any other duty laid on him. For one year he is to be free to stay at home and bring happiness to the wife he has married.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5531D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5531D\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not take a pair of millstones—not even the upper one—as security for a debt, because that would be taking a person’s livelihood as security.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5532E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5532E\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If someone is caught kidnapping a fellow Israelite and treating or selling them as a slave, the kidnapper must die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5533F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5533F\"></sup> You must purge the evil from among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5533G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5533G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In cases of defiling skin diseases, be very careful to do exactly as the Levitical<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5534H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5534H\"></sup> priests instruct you. You must follow carefully what I have commanded them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5534I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5534I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Remember what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God did to Miriam along the way after you came out of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5535J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5535J\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When you make a loan of any kind to your neighbor, do not go into their house to get what is offered to you as a pledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5536K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5536K\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Stay outside and let the neighbor to whom you are making the loan bring the pledge out to you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If the neighbor is poor, do not go to sleep with their pledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5538L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5538L\"></sup> in your possession.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Return their cloak by sunset<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5539M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5539M\"></sup> so that your neighbor may sleep in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5539N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5539N\"></sup> Then they will thank you, and it will be regarded as a righteous act in the sight of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5539O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5539O\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not take advantage of a hired worker who is poor and needy, whether that worker is a fellow Israelite or a foreigner residing in one of your towns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5540P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5540P\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Pay them their wages each day before sunset, because they are poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5541Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5541Q\"></sup> and are counting on it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5541R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5541R\"></sup> Otherwise they may cry to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> against you, and you will be guilty of sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5541S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5541S\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Parents are not to be put to death for their children, nor children put to death for their parents; each will die for their own sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5542T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5542T\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not deprive the foreigner or the fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5543U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5543U\"></sup> of justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5543V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5543V\"></sup> or take the cloak of the widow as a pledge.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Remember that you were slaves in Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5544W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5544W\"></sup> and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God redeemed you from there. That is why I command you to do this.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When you are harvesting in your field and you overlook a sheaf, do not go back to get it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5545X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5545X\"></sup> Leave it for the foreigner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5545Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5545Y\"></sup> the fatherless and the widow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5545Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5545Z\"></sup> so that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God may bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5545AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5545AA\"></sup> you in all the work of your hands.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When you beat the olives from your trees, do not go over the branches a second time.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5546AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5546AB\"></sup> Leave what remains for the foreigner, the fatherless and the widow.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When you harvest the grapes in your vineyard, do not go over the vines again. Leave what remains for the foreigner, the fatherless and the widow.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Remember that you were slaves in Egypt. That is why I command you to do this.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5548AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5548AC\"></sup>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>When people have a dispute, they are to take it to court and the judges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5549A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5549A\"></sup> will decide the case,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5549B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5549B\"></sup> acquitting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5549C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5549C\"></sup> the innocent and condemning the guilty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5549D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5549D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If the guilty person deserves to be beaten,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5550E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5550E\"></sup> the judge shall make them lie down and have them flogged in his presence with the number of lashes the crime deserves,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>but the judge must not impose more than forty lashes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5551F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5551F\"></sup> If the guilty party is flogged more than that, your fellow Israelite will be degraded in your eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5551G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5551G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do not muzzle an ox while it is treading out the grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5552H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5552H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If brothers are living together and one of them dies without a son, his widow must not marry outside the family. Her husband’s brother shall take her and marry her and fulfill the duty of a brother-in-law to her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5553I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5553I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The first son she bears shall carry on the name of the dead brother so that his name will not be blotted out from Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5554J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5554J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>However, if a man does not want to marry his brother’s wife,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5555K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5555K\"></sup> she shall go to the elders at the town gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5555L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5555L\"></sup> and say, “My husband’s brother refuses to carry on his brother’s name in Israel. He will not fulfill the duty of a brother-in-law to me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5555M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5555M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the elders of his town shall summon him and talk to him. If he persists in saying, “I do not want to marry her,”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>his brother’s widow shall go up to him in the presence of the elders, take off one of his sandals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5557N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5557N\"></sup> spit in his face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5557O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5557O\"></sup> and say, “This is what is done to the man who will not build up his brother’s family line.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>That man’s line shall be known in Israel as The Family of the Unsandaled.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If two men are fighting and the wife of one of them comes to rescue her husband from his assailant, and she reaches out and seizes him by his private parts,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>you shall cut off her hand. Show her no pity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5560P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5560P\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not have two differing weights in your bag—one heavy, one light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5561Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5561Q\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not have two differing measures in your house—one large, one small.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You must have accurate and honest weights and measures, so that you may live long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5563R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5563R\"></sup> in the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God detests anyone who does these things, anyone who deals dishonestly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5564S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5564S\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Remember what the Amalekites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5565T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5565T\"></sup> did to you along the way when you came out of Egypt.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When you were weary and worn out, they met you on your journey and attacked all who were lagging behind; they had no fear of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5566U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5566U\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God gives you rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5567V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5567V\"></sup> from all the enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5567W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5567W\"></sup> around you in the land he is giving you to possess as an inheritance, you shall blot out the name of Amalek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5567X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5567X\"></sup> from under heaven. Do not forget!"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>When you have entered the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you as an inheritance and have taken possession of it and settled in it,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>take some of the firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5569A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5569A\"></sup> of all that you produce from the soil of the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you and put them in a basket. Then go to the place the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will choose as a dwelling for his Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5569B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5569B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say to the priest in office at the time, “I declare today to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God that I have come to the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> swore to our ancestors to give us.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The priest shall take the basket from your hands and set it down in front of the altar of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then you shall declare before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God: “My father was a wandering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5572C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5572C\"></sup> Aramean,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5572D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5572D\"></sup> and he went down into Egypt with a few people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5572E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5572E\"></sup> and lived there and became a great nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5572F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5572F\"></sup> powerful and numerous.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But the Egyptians mistreated us and made us suffer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5573G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5573G\"></sup> subjecting us to harsh labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5573H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5573H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then we cried out to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of our ancestors, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> heard our voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5574I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5574I\"></sup> and saw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5574J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5574J\"></sup> our misery,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5574K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5574K\"></sup> toil and oppression.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5574L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5574L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> brought us out of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5575M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5575M\"></sup> with a mighty hand and an outstretched arm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5575N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5575N\"></sup> with great terror and with signs and wonders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5575O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5575O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He brought us to this place and gave us this land, a land flowing with milk and honey;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5576P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5576P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and now I bring the firstfruits of the soil that you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have given me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5577Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5577Q\"></sup>” Place the basket before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and bow down before him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then you and the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5578R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5578R\"></sup> and the foreigners residing among you shall rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5578S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5578S\"></sup> in all the good things the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has given to you and your household.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you have finished setting aside a tenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5579T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5579T\"></sup> of all your produce in the third year, the year of the tithe,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5579U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5579U\"></sup> you shall give it to the Levite, the foreigner, the fatherless and the widow, so that they may eat in your towns and be satisfied.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then say to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God: “I have removed from my house the sacred portion and have given it to the Levite, the foreigner, the fatherless and the widow, according to all you commanded. I have not turned aside from your commands nor have I forgotten any of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5580V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5580V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have not eaten any of the sacred portion while I was in mourning, nor have I removed any of it while I was unclean,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5581W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5581W\"></sup> nor have I offered any of it to the dead. I have obeyed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God; I have done everything you commanded me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Look down from heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5582X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5582X\"></sup> your holy dwelling place, and bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5582Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5582Y\"></sup> your people Israel and the land you have given us as you promised on oath to our ancestors, a land flowing with milk and honey.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God commands you this day to follow these decrees and laws; carefully observe them with all your heart and with all your soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5583Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5583Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You have declared this day that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is your God and that you will walk in obedience to him, that you will keep his decrees, commands and laws—that you will listen to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5584AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5584AA\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has declared this day that you are his people, his treasured possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5585AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5585AB\"></sup> as he promised, and that you are to keep all his commands.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He has declared that he will set you in praise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5586AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5586AC\"></sup> fame and honor high above all the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5586AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5586AD\"></sup> he has made and that you will be a people holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5586AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5586AE\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, as he promised."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Moses and the elders of Israel commanded the people: “Keep all these commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5587A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5587A\"></sup> that I give you today.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When you have crossed the Jordan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5588B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5588B\"></sup> into the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you, set up some large stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5588C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5588C\"></sup> and coat them with plaster.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5588D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5588D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Write on them all the words of this law when you have crossed over to enter the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you, a land flowing with milk and honey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5589E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5589E\"></sup> just as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your ancestors, promised you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when you have crossed the Jordan, set up these stones on Mount Ebal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5590F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5590F\"></sup> as I command you today, and coat them with plaster.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Build there an altar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5591G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5591G\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, an altar of stones. Do not use any iron tool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5591H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5591H\"></sup> on them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Build the altar of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God with fieldstones and offer burnt offerings on it to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Sacrifice fellowship offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5593I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5593I\"></sup> there, eating them and rejoicing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5593J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5593J\"></sup> in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5593K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5593K\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And you shall write very clearly all the words of this law on these stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5594L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5594L\"></sup> you have set up.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5594M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5594M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then Moses and the Levitical<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5595N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5595N\"></sup> priests said to all Israel, “Be silent, Israel, and listen! You have now become the people of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5595O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5595O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and follow his commands and decrees that I give you today.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>On the same day Moses commanded the people:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you have crossed the Jordan, these tribes shall stand on Mount Gerizim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5598P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5598P\"></sup> to bless the people: Simeon, Levi, Judah, Issachar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5598Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5598Q\"></sup> Joseph and Benjamin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5598R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5598R\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And these tribes shall stand on Mount Ebal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5599S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5599S\"></sup> to pronounce curses: Reuben, Gad, Asher, Zebulun, Dan and Naphtali.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The Levites shall recite to all the people of Israel in a loud voice:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who makes an idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5601T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5601T\"></sup>—a thing detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5601U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5601U\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the work of skilled hands—and sets it up in secret.”Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5601V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5601V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who dishonors their father or mother.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5602W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5602W\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who moves their neighbor’s boundary stone.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5603X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5603X\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who leads the blind astray on the road.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5604Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5604Y\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who withholds justice from the foreigner,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5605Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5605Z\"></sup> the fatherless or the widow.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5605AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5605AA\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who sleeps with his father’s wife, for he dishonors his father’s bed.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5606AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5606AB\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who has sexual relations with any animal.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5607AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5607AC\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who sleeps with his sister, the daughter of his father or the daughter of his mother.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5608AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5608AD\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who sleeps with his mother-in-law.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5609AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5609AE\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who kills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5610AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5610AF\"></sup> their neighbor secretly.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5610AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5610AG\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who accepts a bribe to kill an innocent person.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5611AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5611AH\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Cursed is anyone who does not uphold the words of this law by carrying them out.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5612AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5612AI\"></sup>Then all the people shall say, “Amen!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5612AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5612AJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>If you fully obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and carefully follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5613A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5613A\"></sup> all his commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5613B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5613B\"></sup> I give you today, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will set you high above all the nations on earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5613C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5613C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>All these blessings will come on you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5614D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5614D\"></sup> and accompany you if you obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will be blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5615E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5615E\"></sup> in the city and blessed in the country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5615F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5615F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The fruit of your womb will be blessed, and the crops of your land and the young of your livestock—the calves of your herds and the lambs of your flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5616G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5616G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your basket and your kneading trough will be blessed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You will be blessed when you come in and blessed when you go out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5618H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5618H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will grant that the enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5619I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5619I\"></sup> who rise up against you will be defeated before you. They will come at you from one direction but flee from you in seven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5619J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will send a blessing on your barns and on everything you put your hand to. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5620K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5620K\"></sup> you in the land he is giving you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will establish you as his holy people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5621L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5621L\"></sup> as he promised you on oath, if you keep the commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5621M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5621M\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and walk in obedience to him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then all the peoples on earth will see that you are called by the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5622N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5622N\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and they will fear you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will grant you abundant prosperity—in the fruit of your womb, the young of your livestock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5623O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5623O\"></sup> and the crops of your ground—in the land he swore to your ancestors to give you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5623P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5623P\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will open the heavens, the storehouse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5624Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5624Q\"></sup> of his bounty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5624R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5624R\"></sup> to send rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5624S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5624S\"></sup> on your land in season and to bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5624T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5624T\"></sup> all the work of your hands. You will lend to many nations but will borrow from none.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5624U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5624U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make you the head, not the tail. If you pay attention to the commands of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God that I give you this day and carefully follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5625V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5625V\"></sup> them, you will always be at the top, never at the bottom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5625W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5625W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not turn aside from any of the commands I give you today, to the right or to the left,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5626X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5626X\"></sup> following other gods and serving them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>However, if you do not obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5627Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5627Y\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and do not carefully follow all his commands and decrees I am giving you today,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5627Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5627Z\"></sup> all these curses will come on you and overtake you:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5627AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5627AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will be cursed in the city and cursed in the country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5628AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5628AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your basket and your kneading trough will be cursed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5629AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5629AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The fruit of your womb will be cursed, and the crops of your land, and the calves of your herds and the lambs of your flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5630AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5630AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will be cursed when you come in and cursed when you go out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5631AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5631AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will send on you curses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5632AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5632AF\"></sup> confusion and rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5632AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5632AG\"></sup> in everything you put your hand to, until you are destroyed and come to sudden ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5632AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5632AH\"></sup> because of the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5632AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5632AI\"></sup> you have done in forsaking him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will plague you with diseases until he has destroyed you from the land you are entering to possess.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5633AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5633AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike you with wasting disease,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5634AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5634AK\"></sup> with fever and inflammation, with scorching heat and drought,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5634AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5634AL\"></sup> with blight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5634AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5634AM\"></sup> and mildew, which will plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5634AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5634AN\"></sup> you until you perish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5634AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5634AO\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The sky over your head will be bronze, the ground beneath you iron.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5635AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5635AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will turn the rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5636AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5636AQ\"></sup> of your country into dust and powder; it will come down from the skies until you are destroyed.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will cause you to be defeated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5637AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5637AR\"></sup> before your enemies. You will come at them from one direction but flee from them in seven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5637AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5637AS\"></sup> and you will become a thing of horror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5637AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5637AT\"></sup> to all the kingdoms on earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5637AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5637AU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Your carcasses will be food for all the birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5638AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5638AV\"></sup> and the wild animals, and there will be no one to frighten them away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5638AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5638AW\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will afflict you with the boils of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5639AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5639AX\"></sup> and with tumors, festering sores and the itch, from which you cannot be cured.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will afflict you with madness, blindness and confusion of mind.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At midday you will grope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5641AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5641AY\"></sup> about like a blind person in the dark. You will be unsuccessful in everything you do; day after day you will be oppressed and robbed, with no one to rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5641AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5641AZ\"></sup> you.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>You will be pledged to be married to a woman, but another will take her and rape her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5642BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5642BA\"></sup> You will build a house, but you will not live in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5642BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5642BB\"></sup> You will plant a vineyard, but you will not even begin to enjoy its fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5642BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5642BC\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Your ox will be slaughtered before your eyes, but you will eat none of it. Your donkey will be forcibly taken from you and will not be returned. Your sheep will be given to your enemies, and no one will rescue them.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Your sons and daughters will be given to another nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5644BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5644BD\"></sup> and you will wear out your eyes watching for them day after day, powerless to lift a hand.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>A people that you do not know will eat what your land and labor produce, and you will have nothing but cruel oppression<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5645BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5645BE\"></sup> all your days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5645BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5645BF\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The sights you see will drive you mad.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5646BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5646BG\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will afflict your knees and legs with painful boils<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5647BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5647BH\"></sup> that cannot be cured, spreading from the soles of your feet to the top of your head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5647BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5647BI\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will drive you and the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5648BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5648BJ\"></sup> you set over you to a nation unknown to you or your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5648BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5648BK\"></sup> There you will worship other gods, gods of wood and stone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5648BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5648BL\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>You will become a thing of horror,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5649BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5649BM\"></sup> a byword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5649BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5649BN\"></sup> and an object of ridicule<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5649BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5649BO\"></sup> among all the peoples where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will drive you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5649BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5649BP\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>You will sow much seed in the field but you will harvest little,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5650BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5650BQ\"></sup> because locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5650BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5650BR\"></sup> will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5650BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5650BS\"></sup> it.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>You will plant vineyards and cultivate them but you will not drink the wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5651BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5651BT\"></sup> or gather the grapes, because worms will eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5651BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5651BU\"></sup> them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5651BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5651BV\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>You will have olive trees throughout your country but you will not use the oil, because the olives will drop off.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5652BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5652BW\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>You will have sons and daughters but you will not keep them, because they will go into captivity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5653BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5653BX\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Swarms of locusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5654BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5654BY\"></sup> will take over all your trees and the crops of your land.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>The foreigners who reside among you will rise above you higher and higher, but you will sink lower and lower.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5655BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5655BZ\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>They will lend to you, but you will not lend to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5656CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5656CA\"></sup> They will be the head, but you will be the tail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5656CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5656CB\"></sup>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>All these curses will come on you. They will pursue you and overtake you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5657CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5657CC\"></sup> until you are destroyed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5657CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5657CD\"></sup> because you did not obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and observe the commands and decrees he gave you.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>They will be a sign and a wonder to you and your descendants forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5658CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5658CE\"></sup>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Because you did not serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5659CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5659CF\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God joyfully and gladly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5659CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5659CG\"></sup> in the time of prosperity,",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>therefore in hunger and thirst,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5660CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5660CH\"></sup> in nakedness and dire poverty, you will serve the enemies the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sends against you. He will put an iron yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5660CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5660CI\"></sup> on your neck<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5660CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5660CJ\"></sup> until he has destroyed you.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring a nation against you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5661CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5661CK\"></sup> from far away, from the ends of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5661CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5661CL\"></sup> like an eagle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5661CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5661CM\"></sup> swooping down, a nation whose language you will not understand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5661CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5661CN\"></sup>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>a fierce-looking nation without respect for the old<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5662CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5662CO\"></sup> or pity for the young.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>They will devour the young of your livestock and the crops of your land until you are destroyed. They will leave you no grain, new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5663CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5663CP\"></sup> or olive oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5663CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5663CQ\"></sup> nor any calves of your herds or lambs of your flocks until you are ruined.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5663CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5663CR\"></sup>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>They will lay siege<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5664CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5664CS\"></sup> to all the cities throughout your land until the high fortified walls in which you trust fall down. They will besiege all the cities throughout the land the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God is giving you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5664CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5664CT\"></sup>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Because of the suffering your enemy will inflict on you during the siege, you will eat the fruit of the womb, the flesh of the sons and daughters the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has given you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5665CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5665CU\"></sup>",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Even the most gentle and sensitive man among you will have no compassion on his own brother or the wife he loves or his surviving children,",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>and he will not give to one of them any of the flesh of his children that he is eating. It will be all he has left because of the suffering your enemy will inflict on you during the siege of all your cities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5667CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5667CV\"></sup>",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>The most gentle and sensitive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5668CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5668CW\"></sup> woman among you—so sensitive and gentle that she would not venture to touch the ground with the sole of her foot—will begrudge the husband she loves and her own son or daughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5668CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5668CX\"></sup>",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>the afterbirth from her womb and the children she bears. For in her dire need she intends to eat them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5669CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5669CY\"></sup> secretly because of the suffering your enemy will inflict on you during the siege of your cities.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>If you do not carefully follow all the words of this law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5670CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5670CZ\"></sup> which are written in this book, and do not revere<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5670DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5670DA\"></sup> this glorious and awesome name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5670DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5670DB\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God—",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will send fearful plagues on you and your descendants, harsh and prolonged disasters, and severe and lingering illnesses.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>He will bring on you all the diseases of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5672DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5672DC\"></sup> that you dreaded, and they will cling to you.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will also bring on you every kind of sickness and disaster not recorded in this Book of the Law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5673DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5673DD\"></sup> until you are destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5673DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5673DE\"></sup>",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>You who were as numerous as the stars in the sky<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5674DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5674DF\"></sup> will be left but few<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5674DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5674DG\"></sup> in number, because you did not obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>Just as it pleased<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5675DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5675DH\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to make you prosper and increase in number, so it will please<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5675DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5675DI\"></sup> him to ruin and destroy you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5675DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5675DJ\"></sup> You will be uprooted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5675DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5675DK\"></sup> from the land you are entering to possess.",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5676DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5676DL\"></sup> you among all nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5676DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5676DM\"></sup> from one end of the earth to the other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5676DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5676DN\"></sup> There you will worship other gods—gods of wood and stone, which neither you nor your ancestors have known.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5676DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5676DO\"></sup>",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>Among those nations you will find no repose, no resting place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5677DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5677DP\"></sup> for the sole of your foot. There the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will give you an anxious mind, eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5677DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5677DQ\"></sup> weary with longing, and a despairing heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5677DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5677DR\"></sup>",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>You will live in constant suspense, filled with dread both night and day, never sure of your life.",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>In the morning you will say, “If only it were evening!” and in the evening, “If only it were morning!”—because of the terror that will fill your hearts and the sights that your eyes will see.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5679DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5679DS\"></sup>",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will send you back in ships to Egypt on a journey I said you should never make again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5680DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5680DT\"></sup> There you will offer yourselves for sale to your enemies as male and female slaves, but no one will buy you."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>These are the terms of the covenant the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded Moses to make with the Israelites in Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5681A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5681A\"></sup> in addition to the covenant he had made with them at Horeb.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5681B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5681B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Moses summoned all the Israelites and said to them:Your eyes have seen all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> did in Egypt to Pharaoh, to all his officials and to all his land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5682C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5682C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>With your own eyes you saw those great trials, those signs and great wonders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5683D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5683D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But to this day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not given you a mind that understands or eyes that see or ears that hear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5684E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5684E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Yet the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says, “During the forty years that I led<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5685F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5685F\"></sup> you through the wilderness, your clothes did not wear out, nor did the sandals on your feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5685G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5685G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You ate no bread and drank no wine or other fermented drink.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5686H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5686H\"></sup> I did this so that you might know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5686I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5686I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When you reached this place, Sihon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5687J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5687J\"></sup> king of Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5687K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5687K\"></sup> and Og king of Bashan came out to fight against us, but we defeated them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5687L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5687L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We took their land and gave it as an inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5688M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5688M\"></sup> to the Reubenites, the Gadites and the half-tribe of Manasseh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5688N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5688N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Carefully follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5689O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5689O\"></sup> the terms of this covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5689P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5689P\"></sup> so that you may prosper in everything you do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5689Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5689Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>All of you are standing today in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God—your leaders and chief men, your elders and officials, and all the other men of Israel,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>together with your children and your wives, and the foreigners living in your camps who chop your wood and carry your water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5691R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5691R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You are standing here in order to enter into a covenant with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, a covenant the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is making with you this day and sealing with an oath,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>to confirm you this day as his people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5693S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5693S\"></sup> that he may be your God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5693T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5693T\"></sup> as he promised you and as he swore to your fathers, Abraham, Isaac and Jacob.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I am making this covenant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5694U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5694U\"></sup> with its oath, not only with you",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>who are standing here with us today in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God but also with those who are not here today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5695V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5695V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You yourselves know how we lived in Egypt and how we passed through the countries on the way here.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You saw among them their detestable images and idols of wood and stone, of silver and gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5697W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5697W\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Make sure there is no man or woman, clan or tribe among you today whose heart turns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5698X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5698X\"></sup> away from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God to go and worship the gods of those nations; make sure there is no root among you that produces such bitter poison.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5698Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5698Y\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When such a person hears the words of this oath and they invoke a blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5699Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5699Z\"></sup> on themselves, thinking, “I will be safe, even though I persist in going my own way,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5699AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5699AA\"></sup> they will bring disaster on the watered land as well as the dry.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will never be willing to forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5700AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5700AB\"></sup> them; his wrath and zeal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5700AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5700AC\"></sup> will burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5700AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5700AD\"></sup> against them. All the curses written in this book will fall on them, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will blot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5700AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5700AE\"></sup> out their names from under heaven.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will single them out from all the tribes of Israel for disaster,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5701AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5701AF\"></sup> according to all the curses of the covenant written in this Book of the Law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5701AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5701AG\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your children who follow you in later generations and foreigners who come from distant lands will see the calamities that have fallen on the land and the diseases with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has afflicted it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5702AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5702AH\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The whole land will be a burning waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5703AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5703AI\"></sup> of salt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5703AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5703AJ\"></sup> and sulfur—nothing planted, nothing sprouting, no vegetation growing on it. It will be like the destruction of Sodom and Gomorrah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5703AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5703AK\"></sup> Admah and Zeboyim, which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> overthrew in fierce anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5703AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5703AL\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>All the nations will ask: “Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> done this to this land?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5704AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5704AM\"></sup> Why this fierce, burning anger?”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And the answer will be: “It is because this people abandoned the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of their ancestors, the covenant he made with them when he brought them out of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5705AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5705AN\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They went off and worshiped other gods and bowed down to them, gods they did not know, gods he had not given them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger burned against this land, so that he brought on it all the curses written in this book.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5707AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5707AO\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In furious anger and in great wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5708AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5708AP\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> uprooted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5708AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5708AQ\"></sup> them from their land and thrust them into another land, as it is now.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The secret things belong to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5709AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5709AR\"></sup> but the things revealed belong to us and to our children forever, that we may follow all the words of this law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5709AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5709AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>When all these blessings and curses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5710A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5710A\"></sup> I have set before you come on you and you take them to heart wherever the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God disperses you among the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5710B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5710B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and when you and your children return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5711C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5711C\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and obey him with all your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5711D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5711D\"></sup> and with all your soul according to everything I command you today,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will restore your fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5712E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5712E\"></sup> and have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5712F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5712F\"></sup> on you and gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5712G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5712G\"></sup> you again from all the nations where he scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5712H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5712H\"></sup> you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5712I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5712I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Even if you have been banished to the most distant land under the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5713J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5713J\"></sup> from there the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5713K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5713K\"></sup> you and bring you back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5713L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5713L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5714M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5714M\"></sup> you to the land that belonged to your ancestors, and you will take possession of it. He will make you more prosperous and numerous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5714N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5714N\"></sup> than your ancestors.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will circumcise your hearts and the hearts of your descendants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5715O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5715O\"></sup> so that you may love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5715P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5715P\"></sup> him with all your heart and with all your soul, and live.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will put all these curses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5716Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5716Q\"></sup> on your enemies who hate and persecute you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5716R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5716R\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You will again obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and follow all his commands I am giving you today.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will make you most prosperous in all the work of your hands and in the fruit of your womb, the young of your livestock and the crops of your land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5718S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5718S\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will again delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5718T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5718T\"></sup> in you and make you prosperous, just as he delighted in your ancestors,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>if you obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and keep his commands and decrees that are written in this Book of the Law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5719U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5719U\"></sup> and turn to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God with all your heart and with all your soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5719V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5719V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now what I am commanding you today is not too difficult for you or beyond your reach.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5720W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5720W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is not up in heaven, so that you have to ask, “Who will ascend into heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5721X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5721X\"></sup> to get it and proclaim it to us so we may obey it?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5721Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5721Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Nor is it beyond the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5722Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5722Z\"></sup> so that you have to ask, “Who will cross the sea to get it and proclaim it to us so we may obey it?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5722AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5722AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>No, the word is very near you; it is in your mouth and in your heart so you may obey it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5723AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5723AB\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>See, I set before you today life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5724AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5724AC\"></sup> and prosperity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5724AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5724AD\"></sup> death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5724AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5724AE\"></sup> and destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5724AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5724AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For I command you today to love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5725AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5725AG\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, to walk in obedience to him, and to keep his commands, decrees and laws; then you will live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5725AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5725AH\"></sup> and increase, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will bless you in the land you are entering to possess.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if your heart turns away and you are not obedient, and if you are drawn away to bow down to other gods and worship them,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I declare to you this day that you will certainly be destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5727AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5727AI\"></sup> You will not live long in the land you are crossing the Jordan to enter and possess.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This day I call the heavens and the earth as witnesses against you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5728AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5728AJ\"></sup> that I have set before you life and death, blessings and curses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5728AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5728AK\"></sup> Now choose life, so that you and your children may live",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and that you may love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5729AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5729AL\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, listen to his voice, and hold fast to him. For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is your life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5729AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5729AM\"></sup> and he will give<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5729AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5729AN\"></sup> you many years in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5729AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5729AO\"></sup> he swore to give to your fathers, Abraham, Isaac and Jacob."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>Then Moses went out and spoke these words to all Israel:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I am now a hundred and twenty years old<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5731A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5731A\"></sup> and I am no longer able to lead you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5731B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5731B\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has said to me, ‘You shall not cross the Jordan.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5731C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5731C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God himself will cross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5732D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5732D\"></sup> over ahead of you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5732E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5732E\"></sup> He will destroy these nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5732F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5732F\"></sup> before you, and you will take possession of their land. Joshua also will cross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5732G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5732G\"></sup> over ahead of you, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will do to them what he did to Sihon and Og,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5733H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5733H\"></sup> the kings of the Amorites, whom he destroyed along with their land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5734I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5734I\"></sup> them to you, and you must do to them all that I have commanded you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Be strong and courageous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5735J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5735J\"></sup> Do not be afraid or terrified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5735K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5735K\"></sup> because of them, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God goes with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5735L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5735L\"></sup> he will never leave you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5735M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5735M\"></sup> nor forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5735N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5735N\"></sup> you.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then Moses summoned Joshua and said<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5736O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5736O\"></sup> to him in the presence of all Israel, “Be strong and courageous, for you must go with this people into the land that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> swore to their ancestors to give them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5736P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5736P\"></sup> and you must divide it among them as their inheritance.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself goes before you and will be with you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5737Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5737Q\"></sup> he will never leave you nor forsake you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5737R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5737R\"></sup> Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So Moses wrote<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5738S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5738S\"></sup> down this law and gave it to the Levitical priests, who carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5738T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5738T\"></sup> the ark of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and to all the elders of Israel.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Moses commanded them: “At the end of every seven years, in the year for canceling debts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5739U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5739U\"></sup> during the Festival of Tabernacles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5739V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5739V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>when all Israel comes to appear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5740W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5740W\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God at the place he will choose,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5740X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5740X\"></sup> you shall read this law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5740Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5740Y\"></sup> before them in their hearing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Assemble the people—men, women and children, and the foreigners residing in your towns—so they can listen and learn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5741Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5741Z\"></sup> to fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5741AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5741AA\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and follow carefully all the words of this law.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Their children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5742AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5742AB\"></sup> who do not know this law, must hear it and learn to fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God as long as you live in the land you are crossing the Jordan to possess.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Moses, “Now the day of your death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5743AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5743AC\"></sup> is near. Call Joshua<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5743AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5743AD\"></sup> and present yourselves at the tent of meeting, where I will commission him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5743AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5743AE\"></sup>” So Moses and Joshua came and presented themselves at the tent of meeting.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5743AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5743AF\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> appeared at the tent in a pillar of cloud, and the cloud stood over the entrance to the tent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5744AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5744AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Moses: “You are going to rest with your ancestors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5745AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5745AH\"></sup> and these people will soon prostitute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5745AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5745AI\"></sup> themselves to the foreign gods of the land they are entering. They will forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5745AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5745AJ\"></sup> me and break the covenant I made with them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And in that day I will become angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AK\"></sup> with them and forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AL\"></sup> them; I will hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AM\"></sup> my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AN\"></sup> from them, and they will be destroyed. Many disasters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AO\"></sup> and calamities will come on them, and in that day they will ask, ‘Have not these disasters come on us because our God is not with us?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5746AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5746AP\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And I will certainly hide my face in that day because of all their wickedness in turning to other gods.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Now write<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5748AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5748AQ\"></sup> down this song and teach it to the Israelites and have them sing it, so that it may be a witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5748AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5748AR\"></sup> for me against them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When I have brought them into the land flowing with milk and honey, the land I promised on oath to their ancestors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5749AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5749AS\"></sup> and when they eat their fill and thrive, they will turn to other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5749AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5749AT\"></sup> and worship them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5749AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5749AU\"></sup> rejecting me and breaking my covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5749AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5749AV\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And when many disasters and calamities come on them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5750AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5750AW\"></sup> this song will testify against them, because it will not be forgotten by their descendants. I know what they are disposed to do,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5750AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5750AX\"></sup> even before I bring them into the land I promised them on oath.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So Moses wrote<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5751AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5751AY\"></sup> down this song that day and taught it to the Israelites.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave this command<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5752AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5752AZ\"></sup> to Joshua son of Nun: “Be strong and courageous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5752BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5752BA\"></sup> for you will bring the Israelites into the land I promised them on oath, and I myself will be with you.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>After Moses finished writing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5753BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5753BB\"></sup> in a book the words of this law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5753BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5753BC\"></sup> from beginning to end,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>he gave this command to the Levites who carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5754BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5754BD\"></sup> the ark of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Take this Book of the Law and place it beside the ark of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God. There it will remain as a witness against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5755BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5755BE\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For I know how rebellious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5756BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5756BF\"></sup> and stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5756BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5756BG\"></sup> you are. If you have been rebellious against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> while I am still alive and with you, how much more will you rebel after I die!",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Assemble before me all the elders of your tribes and all your officials, so that I can speak these words in their hearing and call the heavens and the earth to testify against them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5757BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5757BH\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For I know that after my death you are sure to become utterly corrupt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5758BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5758BI\"></sup> and to turn from the way I have commanded you. In days to come, disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5758BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5758BJ\"></sup> will fall on you because you will do evil in the sight of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and arouse his anger by what your hands have made.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And Moses recited the words of this song from beginning to end in the hearing of the whole assembly of Israel:"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>Listen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5760A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5760A\"></sup> you heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5760B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5760B\"></sup> and I will speak;hear, you earth, the words of my mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5760C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5760C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let my teaching fall like rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5761D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5761D\"></sup>and my words descend like dew,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5761E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5761E\"></sup>like showers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5761F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5761F\"></sup> on new grass,like abundant rain on tender plants.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5762G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5762G\"></sup> the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5762H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5762H\"></sup>Oh, praise the greatness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5762I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5762I\"></sup> of our God!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He is the Rock,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5763J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5763J\"></sup> his works are perfect,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5763K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5763K\"></sup>and all his ways are just.A faithful God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5763L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5763L\"></sup> who does no wrong,upright<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5763M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5763M\"></sup> and just is he.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5763N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5763N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They are corrupt and not his children;to their shame they are a warped and crooked generation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5764O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5764O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Is this the way you repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5765P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5765P\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,you foolish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5765Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5765Q\"></sup> and unwise people?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5765R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5765R\"></sup>Is he not your Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5765S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5765S\"></sup> your Creator,who made you and formed you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5765T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5765T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember the days of old;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5766U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5766U\"></sup>consider the generations long past.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5766V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5766V\"></sup>Ask your father and he will tell you,your elders, and they will explain to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5766W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5766W\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When the Most High<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5767X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5767X\"></sup> gave the nations their inheritance,when he divided all mankind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5767Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5767Y\"></sup>he set up boundaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5767Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5767Z\"></sup> for the peoplesaccording to the number of the sons of Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5767AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5767AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s portion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5768AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5768AB\"></sup> is his people,Jacob his allotted inheritance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5768AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5768AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In a desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5769AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5769AD\"></sup> land he found him,in a barren and howling waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5769AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5769AE\"></sup>He shielded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5769AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5769AF\"></sup> him and cared for him;he guarded him as the apple of his eye,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5769AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5769AG\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>like an eagle that stirs up its nestand hovers over its young,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5770AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5770AH\"></sup>that spreads its wings to catch themand carries them aloft.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5770AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5770AI\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone led<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5771AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5771AJ\"></sup> him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5771AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5771AK\"></sup>no foreign god was with him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5771AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5771AL\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He made him ride on the heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5772AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5772AM\"></sup> of the landand fed him with the fruit of the fields.He nourished him with honey from the rock,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5772AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5772AN\"></sup>and with oil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5772AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5772AO\"></sup> from the flinty crag,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>with curds and milk from herd and flockand with fattened lambs and goats,with choice rams of Bashan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5773AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5773AP\"></sup>and the finest kernels of wheat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5773AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5773AQ\"></sup>You drank the foaming blood of the grape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5773AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5773AR\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jeshurun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5774AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5774AS\"></sup> grew fat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5774AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5774AT\"></sup> and kicked;filled with food, they became heavy and sleek.They abandoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5774AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5774AU\"></sup> the God who made themand rejected the Rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5774AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5774AV\"></sup> their Savior.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They made him jealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5775AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5775AW\"></sup> with their foreign godsand angered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5775AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5775AX\"></sup> him with their detestable idols.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They sacrificed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5776AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5776AY\"></sup> to false gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5776AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5776AZ\"></sup> which are not God—gods they had not known,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5776BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5776BA\"></sup>gods that recently appeared,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5776BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5776BB\"></sup>gods your ancestors did not fear.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You deserted the Rock, who fathered you;you forgot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5777BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5777BC\"></sup> the God who gave you birth.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saw this and rejected them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5778BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5778BD\"></sup>because he was angered by his sons and daughters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5778BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5778BE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I will hide my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5779BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5779BF\"></sup> from them,” he said,“and see what their end will be;for they are a perverse generation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5779BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5779BG\"></sup>children who are unfaithful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5779BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5779BH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They made me jealous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5780BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5780BI\"></sup> by what is no godand angered me with their worthless idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5780BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5780BJ\"></sup>I will make them envious by those who are not a people;I will make them angry by a nation that has no understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5780BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5780BK\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For a fire will be kindled by my wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5781BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5781BL\"></sup>one that burns down to the realm of the dead below.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5781BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5781BM\"></sup>It will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5781BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5781BN\"></sup> the earth and its harvests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5781BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5781BO\"></sup>and set afire the foundations of the mountains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5781BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5781BP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will heap calamities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5782BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5782BQ\"></sup> on themand spend my arrows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5782BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5782BR\"></sup> against them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I will send wasting famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BS\"></sup> against them,consuming pestilence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BT\"></sup> and deadly plague;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BU\"></sup>I will send against them the fangs of wild beasts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BV\"></sup>the venom of vipers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BW\"></sup> that glide in the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5783BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5783BX\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the street the sword will make them childless;in their homes terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5784BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5784BY\"></sup> will reign.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5784BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5784BZ\"></sup>The young men and young women will perish,the infants and those with gray hair.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5784CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5784CA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I said I would scatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5785CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5785CB\"></sup> themand erase their name from human memory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5785CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5785CC\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>but I dreaded the taunt of the enemy,lest the adversary misunderstand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5786CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5786CD\"></sup>and say, ‘Our hand has triumphed;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not done all this.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5786CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5786CE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They are a nation without sense,there is no discernment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5787CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5787CF\"></sup> in them.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>If only they were wise and would understand this<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5788CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5788CG\"></sup>and discern what their end will be!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5788CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5788CH\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>How could one man chase a thousand,or two put ten thousand to flight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5789CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5789CI\"></sup>unless their Rock had sold them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5789CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5789CJ\"></sup>unless the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had given them up?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5789CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5789CK\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For their rock is not like our Rock,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5790CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5790CL\"></sup>as even our enemies concede.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5790CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5790CM\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Their vine comes from the vine of Sodom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5791CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5791CN\"></sup>and from the fields of Gomorrah.Their grapes are filled with poison,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5791CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5791CO\"></sup>and their clusters with bitterness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5791CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5791CP\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Their wine is the venom of serpents,the deadly poison of cobras.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5792CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5792CQ\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Have I not kept this in reserveand sealed it in my vaults?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5793CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5793CR\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>It is mine to avenge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5794CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5794CS\"></sup> I will repay.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5794CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5794CT\"></sup>In due time their foot will slip;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5794CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5794CU\"></sup>their day of disaster is nearand their doom rushes upon them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5794CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5794CV\"></sup>”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will vindicate his people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5795CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5795CW\"></sup>and relent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5795CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5795CX\"></sup> concerning his servants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5795CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5795CY\"></sup>when he sees their strength is goneand no one is left, slave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5795CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5795CZ\"></sup> or free.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>He will say: “Now where are their gods,the rock they took refuge in,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5796DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5796DA\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>the gods who ate the fat of their sacrificesand drank the wine of their drink offerings?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5797DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5797DB\"></sup>Let them rise up to help you!Let them give you shelter!",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“See now that I myself am he!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DC\"></sup>There is no god besides me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DD\"></sup>I put to death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DE\"></sup> and I bring to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DF\"></sup>I have wounded and I will heal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DG\"></sup>and no one can deliver out of my hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5798DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5798DH\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I lift my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5799DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5799DI\"></sup> to heaven and solemnly swear:As surely as I live forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5799DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5799DJ\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>when I sharpen my flashing sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5800DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5800DK\"></sup>and my hand grasps it in judgment,I will take vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5800DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5800DL\"></sup> on my adversariesand repay those who hate me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5800DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5800DM\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>I will make my arrows drunk with blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5801DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5801DN\"></sup>while my sword devours flesh:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5801DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5801DO\"></sup>the blood of the slain and the captives,the heads of the enemy leaders.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Rejoice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5802DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5802DP\"></sup> you nations, with his people,for he will avenge the blood of his servants;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5802DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5802DQ\"></sup>he will take vengeance on his enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5802DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5802DR\"></sup>and make atonement for his land and people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5802DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5802DS\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Moses came with Joshua<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5803DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5803DT\"></sup> son of Nun and spoke all the words of this song in the hearing of the people.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>When Moses finished reciting all these words to all Israel,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>he said to them, “Take to heart all the words I have solemnly declared to you this day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5805DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5805DU\"></sup> so that you may command<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5805DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5805DV\"></sup> your children to obey carefully all the words of this law.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>They are not just idle words for you—they are your life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5806DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5806DW\"></sup> By them you will live long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5806DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5806DX\"></sup> in the land you are crossing the Jordan to possess.”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>On that same day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> told Moses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5807DY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DY&quot;&gt;DY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5807DY\"></sup>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>“Go up into the Abarim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5808DZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DZ&quot;&gt;DZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5808DZ\"></sup> Range to Mount Nebo<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5808EA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EA&quot;&gt;EA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5808EA\"></sup> in Moab, across from Jericho,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5808EB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EB&quot;&gt;EB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5808EB\"></sup> and view Canaan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5808EC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EC&quot;&gt;EC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5808EC\"></sup> the land I am giving the Israelites as their own possession.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>There on the mountain that you have climbed you will die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5809ED&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ED&quot;&gt;ED&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5809ED\"></sup> and be gathered to your people, just as your brother Aaron died<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5809EE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EE&quot;&gt;EE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5809EE\"></sup> on Mount Hor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5809EF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EF&quot;&gt;EF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5809EF\"></sup> and was gathered to his people.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>This is because both of you broke faith with me in the presence of the Israelites at the waters of Meribah Kadesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5810EG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EG&quot;&gt;EG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5810EG\"></sup> in the Desert of Zin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5810EH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EH&quot;&gt;EH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5810EH\"></sup> and because you did not uphold my holiness among the Israelites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5810EI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EI&quot;&gt;EI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5810EI\"></sup>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Therefore, you will see the land only from a distance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5811EJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EJ&quot;&gt;EJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5811EJ\"></sup> you will not enter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5811EK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EK&quot;&gt;EK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5811EK\"></sup> the land I am giving to the people of Israel.”"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>This is the blessing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5812B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5812B\"></sup> that Moses the man of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5812C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5812C\"></sup> pronounced on the Israelites before his death.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said:“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came from Sinai<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5813D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5813D\"></sup>and dawned over them from Seir;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5813E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5813E\"></sup>he shone forth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5813F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5813F\"></sup> from Mount Paran.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5813G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5813G\"></sup>He came with myriads of holy ones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5813H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5813H\"></sup>from the south, from his mountain slopes.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Surely it is you who love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5814I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5814I\"></sup> the people;all the holy ones are in your hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5814J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5814J\"></sup>At your feet they all bow down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5814K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5814K\"></sup>and from you receive instruction,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>the law that Moses gave us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5815L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5815L\"></sup>the possession of the assembly of Jacob.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5815M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5815M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He was king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5816N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5816N\"></sup> over Jeshurun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5816O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5816O\"></sup>when the leaders of the people assembled,along with the tribes of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Let Reuben live and not die,nor his people be few.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5817P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5817P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And this he said about Judah:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5818Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5818Q\"></sup>“Hear, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the cry of Judah;bring him to his people.With his own hands he defends his cause.Oh, be his help against his foes!”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>About Levi<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5819R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5819R\"></sup> he said:“Your Thummim and Urim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5819S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5819S\"></sup> belongto your faithful servant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5819T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5819T\"></sup>You tested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5819U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5819U\"></sup> him at Massah;you contended with him at the waters of Meribah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5819V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5819V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He said of his father and mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5820W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5820W\"></sup>‘I have no regard for them.’He did not recognize his brothersor acknowledge his own children,but he watched over your wordand guarded your covenant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5820X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5820X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He teaches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5821Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5821Y\"></sup> your precepts to Jacoband your law to Israel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5821Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5821Z\"></sup>He offers incense before you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5821AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5821AA\"></sup>and whole burnt offerings on your altar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5821AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5821AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Bless all his skills, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and be pleased with the work of his hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5822AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5822AC\"></sup>Strike down those who rise against him,his foes till they rise no more.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>About Benjamin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5823AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5823AD\"></sup> he said:“Let the beloved of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> rest secure in him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5823AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5823AE\"></sup>for he shields him all day long,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5823AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5823AF\"></sup>and the one the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5823AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5823AG\"></sup> rests between his shoulders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5823AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5823AH\"></sup>”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>About Joseph<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5824AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5824AI\"></sup> he said:“May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> bless his landwith the precious dew from heaven aboveand with the deep waters that lie below;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5824AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5824AJ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>with the best the sun brings forthand the finest the moon can yield;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>with the choicest gifts of the ancient mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5826AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5826AK\"></sup>and the fruitfulness of the everlasting hills;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>with the best gifts of the earth and its fullnessand the favor of him who dwelt in the burning bush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5827AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5827AL\"></sup>Let all these rest on the head of Joseph,on the brow of the prince among his brothers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5827AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5827AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In majesty he is like a firstborn bull;his horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5828AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5828AN\"></sup> are the horns of a wild ox.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5828AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5828AO\"></sup>With them he will gore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5828AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5828AP\"></sup> the nations,even those at the ends of the earth.Such are the ten thousands of Ephraim;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5828AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5828AQ\"></sup>such are the thousands of Manasseh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5828AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5828AR\"></sup>”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>About Zebulun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5829AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5829AS\"></sup> he said:“Rejoice, Zebulun, in your going out,and you, Issachar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5829AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5829AT\"></sup> in your tents.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will summon peoples to the mountain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5830AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5830AU\"></sup>and there offer the sacrifices of the righteous;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5830AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5830AV\"></sup>they will feast on the abundance of the seas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5830AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5830AW\"></sup>on the treasures hidden in the sand.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>About Gad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5831AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5831AX\"></sup> he said:“Blessed is he who enlarges Gad’s domain!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5831AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5831AY\"></sup>Gad lives there like a lion,tearing at arm or head.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He chose the best land for himself;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5832AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5832AZ\"></sup>the leader’s portion was kept for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5832BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5832BA\"></sup>When the heads of the people assembled,he carried out the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s righteous will,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5832BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5832BB\"></sup>and his judgments concerning Israel.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>About Dan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5833BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5833BC\"></sup> he said:“Dan is a lion’s cub,springing out of Bashan.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>About Naphtali<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5834BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5834BD\"></sup> he said:“Naphtali is abounding with the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and is full of his blessing;he will inherit southward to the lake.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>About Asher<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5835BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5835BE\"></sup> he said:“Most blessed of sons is Asher;let him be favored by his brothers,and let him bathe his feet in oil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5835BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5835BF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The bolts of your gates will be iron and bronze,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5836BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5836BG\"></sup>and your strength will equal your days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5836BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5836BH\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“There is no one like the God of Jeshurun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5837BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5837BI\"></sup>who rides<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5837BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5837BJ\"></sup> across the heavens to help you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5837BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5837BK\"></sup>and on the clouds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5837BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5837BL\"></sup> in his majesty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5837BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5837BM\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The eternal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5838BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5838BN\"></sup> God is your refuge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5838BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5838BO\"></sup>and underneath are the everlasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5838BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5838BP\"></sup> arms.He will drive out your enemies before you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5838BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5838BQ\"></sup>saying, ‘Destroy them!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5838BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5838BR\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So Israel will live in safety;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5839BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5839BS\"></sup>Jacob will dwell securein a land of grain and new wine,where the heavens drop dew.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5839BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5839BT\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Blessed are you, Israel!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5840BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5840BU\"></sup>Who is like you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5840BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5840BV\"></sup>a people saved by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5840BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5840BW\"></sup>He is your shield and helper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5840BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5840BX\"></sup>and your glorious sword.Your enemies will cower before you,and you will tread on their heights.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5840BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5840BY\"></sup>”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Then Moses climbed Mount Nebo<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5841A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5841A\"></sup> from the plains of Moab to the top of Pisgah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5841B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5841B\"></sup> across from Jericho.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5841C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5841C\"></sup> There the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5841D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5841D\"></sup> him the whole land—from Gilead to Dan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5841E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5841E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>all of Naphtali, the territory of Ephraim and Manasseh, all the land of Judah as far as the Mediterranean Sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5842F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5842F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>the Negev<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5843G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5843G\"></sup> and the whole region from the Valley of Jericho, the City of Palms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5843H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5843H\"></sup> as far as Zoar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5843I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5843I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “This is the land I promised on oath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5844J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5844J\"></sup> to Abraham, Isaac and Jacob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5844K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5844K\"></sup> when I said, ‘I will give it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5844L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5844L\"></sup> to your descendants.’ I have let you see it with your eyes, but you will not cross<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5844M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5844M\"></sup> over into it.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Moses the servant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5845N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5845N\"></sup> died<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5845O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5845O\"></sup> there in Moab, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had said.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He buried him in Moab, in the valley opposite Beth Peor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5846P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5846P\"></sup> but to this day no one knows where his grave is.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5846Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5846Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Moses was a hundred and twenty years old<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5847R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5847R\"></sup> when he died, yet his eyes were not weak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5847S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5847S\"></sup> nor his strength gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5847T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5847T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Israelites grieved for Moses in the plains of Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5848U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5848U\"></sup> thirty days,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5848V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5848V\"></sup> until the time of weeping and mourning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5848W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5848W\"></sup> was over.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now Joshua son of Nun was filled with the spirit of wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5849X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5849X\"></sup> because Moses had laid his hands on him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5849Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5849Y\"></sup> So the Israelites listened to him and did what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded Moses.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Since then, no prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5850Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5850Z\"></sup> has risen in Israel like Moses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5850AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5850AA\"></sup> whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> knew face to face,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5850AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5850AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>who did all those signs and wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5851AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5851AC\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent him to do in Egypt—to Pharaoh and to all his officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5851AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5851AD\"></sup> and to his whole land.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For no one has<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5852AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5852AE\"></sup> ever shown the mighty power or performed the awesome deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-5852AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-5852AF\"></sup> that Moses did in the sight of all Israel."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;